NK073(pu)001:1: // slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i lam rim chen mo bzhugs so //
NK073(pu)001:3: dpal gyi dpal gsum nyid ldan rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes 'dus ma byas /
NK073(pu)001:4: ma btsal lnga rdzogs skyon bral mi shigs dbyings nyid ye shes 'du 'bral med /
NK073(pu)001:5: lnga yi rdo rje grub nyid gnyis med ngang gsal mi g.yo mi sems sems chen po /
NK073(pu)001:6: bdud sde bzhi bcom dpa' bo rang nyid lha yi lha la gnyis med mos /
NK073(pu)001:7: gsang ba'i bdag pos mngon shes nas //
NK073(pu)001:8: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK073(pu)001:9: mi yi skal ldan 'dus pa la //
NK073(pu)001:10: dang po ji ltar lung bstan dus //
NK073(pu)001:11: rgyal bu'i rigs can ltas shar ba //
NK073(pu)001:12: 'brel bas snang la mngon brtags pa //
NK073(pu)001:13: thugs kyi dgongs pa mngon rtogs te //
NK073(pu)001:14: de nyid sgo nas de nyid grub //
NK073(pu)001:15: brtan pa'i dngos grub de nas 'thob //
NK073(pu)001:16: don dam bcu kyang de nas rgyas //
NK073(pu)001:18: smon pa'i lha dang de ru mjal //
NK073(pu)001:19: de nas rdo rje gdan steng gi //
NK073(pu)001:20: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams su //
NK073(pu)001:21: pho brang dam pa rin chen nang //
NK073(pu)001:22: bkra shis dam pa'i khang bu ru //
NK073(pu)001:23: ku ku r+aa dz+aan+d+re b+hu ti //
NK073(pu)001:24: sing ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK073(pu)001:25: sras mo go ma sa la sogs //
NK073(pu)001:26: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:27: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon sgrub te //
NK073(pu)001:28: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:29: de phyir sangs rgyas mtshan thob nges //
NK073(pu)001:30: dam pa'i rig can d+r+wa ma dang //
NK073(pu)001:31: de rjes ma 'ongs skal ldan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:32: stong phrag brgya yi rgyud dag las //
NK073(pu)001:33: gshegs shul lam mchog 'di bsdus te //
NK073(pu)001:34: snyigs ma rgyud drag dus kyi tshe //
NK073(pu)001:35: dus kyis 'dul phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:36: spyan bzang 'gro mthu med pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:37: mig bu bral ba'i nyams stor nas //
NK073(pu)001:38: bgrod cing phyin par mi nus bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:39: rtsing por dmu rgod rang nyams kyis //
NK073(pu)001:40: gsang ba'i snying por mi 'gyur te //
NK073(pu)001:42: de bas bla ma lung bzhin bkur //
NK073(pu)001:43: brtag spyo zhe gcod bzod byas te //
NK073(pu)001:44: mthong ba'i gdung ba khur mi lta //
NK073(pu)001:45: de kun yun gyi don du bzod //
NK073(pu)001:46: dka' bas brten nas rdo rje rgyal //
NK073(pu)001:47: nyams kyi gnang ba thob 'gyur te //
NK073(pu)001:48: de tshe rgyud chen gzhung gi yon //
NK073(pu)001:49: phul na thugs kyi nying khu ster //
NK073(pu)001:50: de yis bzhon pa zang 'gro bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:51: gsang ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs zhon pas //
NK073(pu)001:52: mthong 'jug mthar phyin bzhi bgrod nas //
NK073(pu)001:53: ye shes snying po'i gnas su phyin //
NK073(pu)001:54: de bas rdo rje gnyer ldan ma //
NK073(pu)001:55: spyang grung sems sra mkha' 'gro ma'i //
NK073(pu)001:56: gsang sngags ltas ston spyo ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:57: ci nas brtags te bzang ldan na //
NK073(pu)001:58: mi ltog brtan byas brtas pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:59: shi sha gang yin lag tu gtad //
NK073(pu)001:60: ngan pa'i rtags mthong mngon shes pas //
NK073(pu)001:61: 'dod pa phra mo rgyur byed dang //
NK073(pu)001:62: khe dang grags pa che ba'i rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:63: byed cing bcud chen 'dzag dang dbo //
NK073(pu)001:64: mi chags ma rungs byed pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:65: zang zing mtha' gtong dbus 'ching dang //
NK073(pu)001:66: g.yon can ngo dga' lhag sprad skur //
NK073(pu)001:67: lkog na rang dgar byed pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:68: ngag la rigs nges bsam mi nges //
NK073(pu)001:71: pho mo tan+t+ra ma basngagasa la //
NK073(pu)001:72: bskal par grib bzhin 'khor gyur yang //
NK073(pu)001:73: thugs kyi bde ba spro mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:75: de min be'u sbrel g.yang skyur bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:77: ma rtogs spros na dur khrod gling //
NK073(pu)001:79: sha za srog la 'bebs shing ltung //
NK073(pu)001:80: de ltar brtags pas bskal ldan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:81: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK073(pu)001:83: bar chad med sgrub rnam par smin //
NK073(pu)001:84: dbang bskur phyag rgya lhun grub lam //
NK073(pu)001:85: mngon byang rim par brjod par bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:86: de la dang po nyid spros pas //
NK073(pu)001:87: de nyid de yis shes bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:88: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK073(pu)001:89: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK073(pu)001:90: 'khor ba sems phyir bdag med pas //
NK073(pu)001:91: de phyir de bzhin gshegs bsam yas //
NK073(pu)001:92: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin mi dmigs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:93: mya ngan 'das pa yod ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:94: de ltar rigs dang rgyu med pas //
NK073(pu)001:95: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo la //
NK073(pu)001:96: so so'i rang bzhin nges shes na //
NK073(pu)001:97: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK073(pu)001:98: yang dag gshegs dang log rtogs gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:99: ngo bo nyid kyis gnas 'gyur na //
NK073(pu)001:100: de la bcos shing bsgyur du med //
NK073(pu)001:101: 'ching bu rin chen bzhi mi rigs //
NK073(pu)001:102: de bas de lta'ang 'di bzhin bas //
NK073(pu)001:103: ma rig log rtogs zhags pa'i rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:104: las dang nyon mongs brgyad rkyen kyis //
NK073(pu)001:105: bcud gnyis 'khor lo gnas su bskyar //
NK073(pu)001:106: rten dang 'dod pa tha dad pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:107: bde sdug gdung bas nyam thag bral //
NK073(pu)001:108: rtsom med bzhi 'dus kun tu nyams //
NK073(pu)001:109: rang bzhin nyid ni nyams pa med //
NK073(pu)001:110: de lta'ang rgyal po phru gu 'khyams //
NK073(pu)001:111: de bzhin rigs la 'gyur med pas //
NK073(pu)001:112: shul don rang las gzhin min phyir //
NK073(pu)001:113: 'phrul dag'i tshul te gzhan las min //
NK073(pu)001:114: de'ang rnam gsum gnas tshul bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:115: 'bru lngar gnas pa'i thabs chen po //
NK073(pu)001:116: 'gro ba kun las rang bzhin gnas //
NK073(pu)001:117: dkyil 'khor bzhi dang srog shing gsum //
NK073(pu)001:118: gnas nas ka li sgra dbyangs ldan //
NK073(pu)001:119: e wam ma ya mkha' ldan dang //
NK073(pu)001:120: snying po rlung sgrom gnas na yod //
NK073(pu)001:122: de don de ni chos de dang //
NK073(pu)001:123: ye shes yon tan las nyid dengs //
NK073(pu)001:124: rnal 'byor lam rim rang bzhin gnas //
NK073(pu)001:125: snod kyi 'od dbyibs phrin las bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:126: thig le bsnyen sgrub rang bzhin ldan //
NK073(pu)001:127: bzhi brgyad shi ra ma d+ha la //
NK073(pu)001:128: ram yam g.yas g.yon sbyin sreg ldan //
NK073(pu)001:129: gnas bzhi'i 'byung ba'ang las bzhi ste //
NK073(pu)001:130: gsang ba'i mkha' la rang bzhin ldan //
NK073(pu)001:131: gnas rten rtsa dang thig le la //
NK073(pu)001:132: bcu dbang lnga gsum dbang rnams ldan //
NK073(pu)001:133: gsang ba nang gi 'dod yon dang //
NK073(pu)001:134: dam rdzas rang ldan mchod pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:135: de dag rang gnas mi 'da' bas //
NK073(pu)001:136: rang bzhin gnas pa'i sa ma ya //
NK073(pu)001:137: rang bzhin phyi nang gsang ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:138: 'du byed spyod pa ngang gis gnas //
NK073(pu)001:139: chags pas khams 'grub gcig shos kyis //
NK073(pu)001:140: rang bzhin ye shes 'grub byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:141: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag kun //
NK073(pu)001:142: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lngar grags sogs //
NK073(pu)001:143: dngos kun chags dang snang tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:144: las dang ngo bo 'bras bur gnas //
NK073(pu)001:145: chu zla sgyu ma sprul pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:146: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK073(pu)001:147: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres gsal //
NK073(pu)001:149: sa dang lam dang 'bras bu rnams //
NK073(pu)001:150: gang yang rigs rgyud rtags min pas //
NK073(pu)001:151: sems phyir kun kyang de de dang //
NK073(pu)001:152: gzugs gnyis mtshan gsum yod dang med //
NK073(pu)001:153: gnas rigs sde cha yod med rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:154: gnyis yul bral bzhin de 'dir 'bru chad /
NK073(pu)001:156: bdun dang gsum phyir don dam dang //
NK073(pu)001:157: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen dang //
NK073(pu)001:158: de kun ngo bo nyid rgyud gnas //
NK073(pu)001:159: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs ba //
NK073(pu)001:160: snang ba nyid sku chen po yin //
NK073(pu)001:161: rang bzhin ngang gis de ltar gnas //
NK073(pu)001:162: de las gzhan pa'i thob bya med //
NK073(pu)001:163: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa med //
NK073(pu)001:164: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo ste //
NK073(pu)001:166: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:167: rang byung chen po kun tu khyab //
NK073(pu)001:168: rang byung de nyid dngos med par //
NK073(pu)001:169: kun gyi phyag rgya rgyud yin phyin //
NK073(pu)001:170: de lta bu yi ngang du gnas //
NK073(pu)001:171: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK073(pu)001:172: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:173: ming grangs med pa'i rgyu nyid dang //
NK073(pu)001:174: yongs su rdzogs pa zhes kyang brjod //
NK073(pu)001:175: gsum pa dngos po zhen pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:177: ye nas rigs rgyud rtags min pas //
NK073(pu)001:178: so so'i gzugs sgra dri ro reg /
NK073(pu)001:179: chos kyi bye brag tha snyad kun //
NK073(pu)001:182: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK073(pu)001:183: rgyal 'gros mi mdzad ma bcos pa //
NK073(pu)001:184: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med ngang //
NK073(pu)001:185: de min zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK073(pu)001:186: tha snyad gnyis pa bsam brjod 'das //
NK073(pu)001:187: yul dang shes rab snang ba yang //
NK073(pu)001:188: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK073(pu)001:189: rgyu 'bras snang yang gnyis pa med //
NK073(pu)001:190: phyi nang gsal ba'ang de nyid ngang //
NK073(pu)001:191: de ltar ye shes rang gnas pa //
NK073(pu)001:192: lam dang 'bras bu kun dngos po //
NK073(pu)001:193: 'brel pa bdag phyir thabs chen pos //
NK073(pu)001:194: mngon byed rang las 'byung bar zad //
NK073(pu)001:195: ye shes rang la gnas pa'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NK073(pu)001:197: // lhun grub ngang nas phyag 'tshal te //
NK073(pu)001:198: dang po lam mchog bshad par bya //
NK073(pu)001:199: yang dag rang gnas mthong 'dod dgos //
NK073(pu)001:200: dus snod rgyu rkyen thabs grangs dngos //
NK073(pu)001:201: spyon yon drod rtags tshad dang skyon //
NK073(pu)001:202: yan lag spros pa'i rtsa bar bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:203: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK073(pu)001:205: blun po mun sprul blo can te //
NK073(pu)001:206: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK073(pu)001:207: de bas ma rig ling tog mig /
NK073(pu)001:208: ldong pas rdo rje thur ma mkhan //
NK073(pu)001:209: mnyes thob sngon byas gzhung thos te //
NK073(pu)001:210: spyan dbye dkyil 'khor mthong byas dgos //
NK073(pu)001:211: de yang rang bzhin sbyangs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:212: snod du gyur pa nye ring phyir //
NK073(pu)001:213: rim dang cig char bzhi cha yis //
NK073(pu)001:215: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK073(pu)001:216: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:218: ring ba'ang rim dang cig char te //
NK073(pu)001:220: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:221: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK073(pu)001:222: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK073(pu)001:223: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK073(pu)001:224: lam stegs sngon du rdzogs par sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:225: de phyir ma nges rigs mchog nas //
NK073(pu)001:226: mun pa'i shes pa sa de nyid //
NK073(pu)001:227: rang bzhin rgyu yi myong bar bshad //
NK073(pu)001:228: phal pa'i sems brgyad mthar gnas tshe //
NK073(pu)001:229: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:230: bshes gnyen kun la lung gnyis thob //
NK073(pu)001:231: yon tan mthong dang skyon mthong dang //
NK073(pu)001:232: de yi skye rmongs brod pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:233: gnyis pa'i rgyu ru gsungs pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:234: de dag gsang sogs dmigs pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:235: skad cig 'phel ba de ma thag /
NK073(pu)001:236: drug las r+ts+wa me bzhin g.yos te //
NK073(pu)001:237: gzhi yi theg pa dang por zhog /
NK073(pu)001:238: de nas rim gyis bgrod bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:239: rgyu nas rkyen gyis 'phar ba ste //
NK073(pu)001:240: rnal 'byor rgyud la gnas pa la //
NK073(pu)001:241: 'di ston mgon la lung thos pas //
NK073(pu)001:242: de ji bzhin du gnyis dang bzhis //
NK073(pu)001:244: gzhi de'i khung du chud smon pas //
NK073(pu)001:245: lhag pa gzugs brnyan 'jug pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:246: mchog gi dam tshig de ru phyin //
NK073(pu)001:247: rigs nges 'gyur la phan pa bcu //
NK073(pu)001:248: nus pa gnyis kyi byin rlabs bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:249: rang gi spyan mchog 'byed la brtson //
NK073(pu)001:250: rgyu yi dkyil 'khor mthong bya'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:251: thos bsam dam pa len par byed //
NK073(pu)001:252: kha cig dus mtha'i cig char ba //
NK073(pu)001:253: bskal pa rdul snyed sngon po bas //
NK073(pu)001:254: thun mong de snyed sbyangs pa'i mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:255: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i don zhugs pas //
NK073(pu)001:257: rim gyis sbya la cig char ro //
NK073(pu)001:258: la la dbang po rnon po dag /
NK073(pu)001:259: theg pa chen po gnyis 'jug ste //
NK073(pu)001:260: ma sbyangs grub pa gsum phyir gyis //
NK073(pu)001:261: mtha' rten myur rno rgya che yangs //
NK073(pu)001:262: zab don rgyu yi gang zag ste //
NK073(pu)001:263: nyid kyang rkyen dang rim pa bas //
NK073(pu)001:264: phye bas rgyu 'bras chen po rnams //
NK073(pu)001:266: de de'ang rang sems dam pa'i ngos //
NK073(pu)001:267: bshes gnyen rnams dang ngo bos 'brel //
NK073(pu)001:268: de ldan bya byed snod bcud du //
NK073(pu)001:269: chen po lung dang 'brel pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:270: mgon dang bya byed thugs rjes 'brel //
NK073(pu)001:271: de phyir mchog lung rdo rje rnams //
NK073(pu)001:272: dang mjal byed phyir rgyu rkyen drug /
NK073(pu)001:273: ldan pas ma nges 'jug pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:274: dbang po ci bzhin mos rkyen gyis //
NK073(pu)001:276: rnal 'byor theg pa sbyong bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:278: sngon bzhin g.yo smon 'jug sems sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:279: gnas bas mthar phyir byed pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:280: ltos par ring bas dus nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:281: ma nges pa nas 'brel rgyu rkyen //
NK073(pu)001:282: ldan pas rnal 'byor mchog sbyor ba //
NK073(pu)001:283: mun pa'i zer tshul r+ts+wa me ltar //
NK073(pu)001:284: g.yo smon 'jug pa'ang sngon bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:286: gzhung nyid ngang tshul rang bzhin sogs //
NK073(pu)001:287: snod yon ldan pas bslab pa la //
NK073(pu)001:288: gnas pa dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK073(pu)001:289: 'jug pa bzhi yi yan lag mchog /
NK073(pu)001:290: dang po ched du gnyer bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:291: gang de thos pas tshol ba'i tshe //
NK073(pu)001:292: rgyu gnyis rkyen gyis bzod thob dang //
NK073(pu)001:293: rang bzhin ngang gis bzod thob pas //
NK073(pu)001:294: re smon sems kyis nyan brtson sbyar //
NK073(pu)001:295: gang dag mnyam bsam shes rab che //
NK073(pu)001:296: nyan cing thos 'dzin bsam pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:297: bsam pa'i tshe na rtog dpyod pa //
NK073(pu)001:298: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:299: mkhan po lung dag man ngag bcas //
NK073(pu)001:300: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod //
NK073(pu)001:301: rang bzhin bdun dang mtshungs ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:302: gcig shos rgyu ru nges pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:303: de ltar ldan pas spyan 'tshol tshe //
NK073(pu)001:304: gtan tshigs rnams kyis smal byas te //
NK073(pu)001:305: nor ba'i shes rab mig gsal nas //
NK073(pu)001:306: ma nor mig la blang bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:307: gzhi dang gtan tshigs 'grub pa'i don //
NK073(pu)001:308: rnam gsum snga ma'i gzhi ru bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:309: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK073(pu)001:311: gsung lnga bstan pa'i de kho na //
NK073(pu)001:313: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig /
NK073(pu)001:314: brjod pa lngas mtshon 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK073(pu)001:315: de la gtan tshigs dngos lnga yis //
NK073(pu)001:316: brda sprod rjes su 'jug bstan pa //
NK073(pu)001:317: bsreg bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:318: dngos lngas legs par brtags te dbab //
NK073(pu)001:319: de yang yongs su brtag gzhi ni //
NK073(pu)001:320: dbang po yul du snang ba kun //
NK073(pu)001:321: yul rnams yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:322: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:323: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:326: ming dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:327: log rtog so so'i rang spyi mtshan //
NK073(pu)001:328: ji ltar gnas pa spyad par bya //
NK073(pu)001:329: dngos gzhis zhen dngos dus gsum chos //
NK073(pu)001:330: skad cig ma lus la rdzogs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:331: de dngos mthong bar yang dag par //
NK073(pu)001:332: rig bzhin kun kyang de ltar shes //
NK073(pu)001:333: kun brtags shes pa bar mar 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:334: spyi yul lus med grib ma bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:335: med pas mi btub rang nyid la //
NK073(pu)001:336: mi btub mdzub mo bzhin dgos pas //
NK073(pu)001:337: gnyen po med pas dag min zhing //
NK073(pu)001:338: bar ma'i yul phyir nges tshig 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:339: de ltar lnga yi de de la //
NK073(pu)001:340: de de'i rang bzhin brtag bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:341: rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:342: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK073(pu)001:343: nges lung yin phyir chos tshur ston //
NK073(pu)001:344: brjod dang 'dra bar brda sprod pas //
NK073(pu)001:345: ngo bo nyid kyi bshad pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:346: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK073(pu)001:347: yang na sa gnas mig ldan pa //
NK073(pu)001:348: rang bzhin shugs kyi skye med don //
NK073(pu)001:349: ma btsal ngang gis snang byed pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:350: brjod med don gyi brjod dang 'dra //
NK073(pu)001:351: gang dag gzugs dang rnal 'byor gyis //
NK073(pu)001:352: mthong thos la sogs rang bzhin brda //
NK073(pu)001:353: dpa' bo'i brda dang dgos pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:354: rang gi ting 'dzin gyis brda sprod //
NK073(pu)001:355: dper na sa 'og gser rlangs dang //
NK073(pu)001:356: me long nyi ma ngad bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:357: kun kyang rig phyir rang bzhin sprod //
NK073(pu)001:358: rang bzhin ngang gis brjod 'drar snang //
NK073(pu)001:359: kun kyang brag cha'i sgra bzhin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:360: grags stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung //
NK073(pu)001:361: sgra thos nyid kyis de nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:362: so sor ma brtag 'jal bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:363: so so'i skad du brda sprod ltar //
NK073(pu)001:364: tshig dbyangs snyan po'i ngag lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:365: mos spyod grol bzhin brjod pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:366: brda sprod yongs su grol bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:367: dang po rgyud la tha dad phyir //
NK073(pu)001:368: gang mos grol ba yod med kyang //
NK073(pu)001:369: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK073(pu)001:370: rang byung kun ngam 'grub byed phyir //
NK073(pu)001:371: mi dmigs ngang las dmigs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:372: cho 'phrul tshig gis mtshon byar bya //
NK073(pu)001:373: gsung lnga thos pa lnga tshul yang //
NK073(pu)001:374: rjes su tshig gis mtshon par byed //
NK073(pu)001:375: ngo bo snang tshig rang snang tshig /
NK073(pu)001:376: ldem dgongs tshig dang bkri drang rgyud //
NK073(pu)001:377: 'dod rkyen tshig dang rdo rje'i tshig /
NK073(pu)001:378: rang rig mngon gsal tshig gis mtshon //
NK073(pu)001:379: thams cad gsang sngags ngo bo nyid //
NK073(pu)001:380: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:381: dbyer med ngang du gnas pa la //
NK073(pu)001:382: ye shes rtogs pa'i don bya'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:383: phyogs dang dbus su gnas par bya //
NK073(pu)001:384: kun la de ltar 'byor par gyis //
NK073(pu)001:385: yi ge tshig dang sgra spangs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:386: brjod med ngang du gnas pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:387: gsung nyid rang bzhin med pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:388: chos rnams thams cad ye nas dag /
NK073(pu)001:389: thams cad thugs su gyur pas na //
NK073(pu)001:390: sgra dang tshig tu gnas pa min //
NK073(pu)001:392: yang dag shes pas rab brtags na //
NK073(pu)001:393: rang bzhin med la cir yang snang //
NK073(pu)001:394: snang ba nyid na dbyings yin te //
NK073(pu)001:395: de ltar rtog pa'i shes pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:396: kun la dbang bsgyur rang dbang can //
NK073(pu)001:397: thams cad tshig gi sgra ltar gnas //
NK073(pu)001:398: 'di ni ye shes gsung mchog yin //
NK073(pu)001:399: chos rnams bsam gyis mi khyab ste //
NK073(pu)001:400: mtha' dang dbus med kun tu khyab //
NK073(pu)001:401: khyab dang khyab med rdo rje'i sku //
NK073(pu)001:402: sgra skad sna tshogs bsgrags pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:403: dngos po med la dngos po'i sgra //
NK073(pu)001:404: ji ltar pi wam lag thogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:406: dngos po med de de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:407: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:408: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK073(pu)001:409: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK073(pu)001:410: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK073(pu)001:411: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:412: ming dang tshig tu brtag nas ston //
NK073(pu)001:413: ji snyed mang po don brjod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:414: rdo rje gsung la spros pa med //
NK073(pu)001:415: spros med de nyid sna tshogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:416: kun la brda 'jal ye shes gsung //
NK073(pu)001:417: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK073(pu)001:418: thams cad pad+ma chags med pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:419: dbang po rnam gnyis bsrubs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:420: mkha' la nyi zla dus gcig shar //
NK073(pu)001:421: mi 'jigs tshul du zil mnan mthong //
NK073(pu)001:422: de phyir gtan tshigs las ma brjod //
NK073(pu)001:423: de lta mod kyang bsdu na gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:424: bzhi rjes mi spyod gcig rjes spyod //
NK073(pu)001:425: rnam gnyis tshul gyi mthong byed pas //
NK073(pu)001:426: dbang po gnyis po mthun sbyar ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:427: de la snga mas go byed pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:428: sems can ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:429: ye nas byang chub snying por gnas //
NK073(pu)001:430: de phyir spyod pa'i bya byed med //
NK073(pu)001:431: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon te //
NK073(pu)001:432: sangs rgyas kyis kyang bstan par dka' //
NK073(pu)001:433: rgyal ba'i sras po cang mi gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:434: ma gsungs pa ni rgya cher bshad //
NK073(pu)001:435: 'chad dang mnyan pa gnyis ka med //
NK073(pu)001:436: dpyod pa zhugs na rtog pa'i gzhi //
NK073(pu)001:437: rtog pa zhugs na dmigs pa'i rten //
NK073(pu)001:438: dmigs pa zhugs na 'dzin pa'i gzung //
NK073(pu)001:440: de bas gser ltar gser bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:441: bdag phyir bya byed mi dmis pas //
NK073(pu)001:443: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong //
NK073(pu)001:444: sus kyang ma bcing bcings med de //
NK073(pu)001:445: bcing bar bya ba'ang yod ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:446: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:447: grol bar mi 'dod bcings dang bral //
NK073(pu)001:448: so sor gang la'ang rtog med pas //
NK073(pu)001:449: so sor snang ba kun rtog phyir //
NK073(pu)001:450: so sor rtog pa'i mchog nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:451: btags pa med pa'i bla dwags yin //
NK073(pu)001:452: kha cig phyi mas grol byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:453: brjod pa'i dngos po spyod yul la //
NK073(pu)001:454: so sor rtog pa'i gtan tshigs rkyen //
NK073(pu)001:455: don dang mthun dang mi mthun pas //
NK073(pu)001:456: phyi ma mi mthun mtshon byed ltar //
NK073(pu)001:457: chos kun mtha' las 'das pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:458: mtha' dag yang dag don med pas //
NK073(pu)001:460: rang gi ngo bo bstan par dka' //
NK073(pu)001:462: mdor na ji ltar brtags bsam bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:463: 'gyur ba kun gyi ngo bor ston //
NK073(pu)001:464: de mtshon ci yang yin pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:465: sems chos ci yang ma yin no //
NK073(pu)001:466: de phyir ma yin kun yin pas //
NK073(pu)001:467: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK073(pu)001:468: mtha' kun phyogs su ma chad phyir //
NK073(pu)001:469: mtha' dang bral phyir ma bral ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:470: gang yang ma spang mi ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:471: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:472: ngo bo phebs pas rgyas par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:473: cig shos mthun par bstan pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:474: bye brag bsdus pas kun khyab gsum //
NK073(pu)001:475: de ldan rnam pa bsam yas pas //
NK073(pu)001:476: cha tsam brjod pa 'di lta mod //
NK073(pu)001:477: chos rnams yongs kyis dag pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:478: rnam bzhi tshul gyis don rtogs mngon //
NK073(pu)001:479: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK073(pu)001:480: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam nyid kyis //
NK073(pu)001:481: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK073(pu)001:482: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:483: byin gyis rlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK073(pu)001:484: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK073(pu)001:485: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK073(pu)001:486: nyid la dbang bsgyur nyid spyod phyir //
NK073(pu)001:487: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK073(pu)001:488: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK073(pu)001:490: yang dag shes bas rab brtag na //
NK073(pu)001:491: rang bzhin med la cir yang snang //
NK073(pu)001:492: snang ba nyid na dbyings nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:493: gshegs sku sgyu mar snang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:494: log rtog sgyu mar snang ba gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:495: gzhi rtsa med de rang bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:496: rigs dang rgyud du brtag tu med //
NK073(pu)001:497: rigs dang kha dog dbyibs med la //
NK073(pu)001:498: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad snang //
NK073(pu)001:499: snang ba nyid na chos kyi sku //
NK073(pu)001:501: nyon mongs rang dang spyi bstan pas //
NK073(pu)001:502: mtshan nyid ma nor rab rtogs na //
NK073(pu)001:503: rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:504: de phyir rang spyi'i gtan tshigs gces //
NK073(pu)001:505: mtha' dang dbus med du ma bral //
NK073(pu)001:506: gang yang min te de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:507: dbyer med par yi tshul rtogs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:508: mtha' dang bral ba de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:509: 'byung ba chen po lnga rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:510: rang bzhin med pas gzhig pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:511: gcig la'ang lnga lngar dbye bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:512: mun gyi dbyings su thim par bya //
NK073(pu)001:513: mus gnyis smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK073(pu)001:514: nam mkha' gzung du med pa ltar //
NK073(pu)001:515: snang srid thams cad de dang 'dra //
NK073(pu)001:516: rten pa gnyen 'khrus gzugs med rlung //
NK073(pu)001:517: gsal bsreg me ltar shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:518: de bzhin phung po dbang yul lnga //
NK073(pu)001:519: nyon mongs kha dog la sogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:520: don dang ngo bo gcig ma 'dres //
NK073(pu)001:521: de phyir de yi mtshon rtogs byed //
NK073(pu)001:522: gtan tshigs gtan tshigs brjod pa rnams //
NK073(pu)001:523: bsgrub bya gang yin shes don la //
NK073(pu)001:524: nges tshig ngo bo mtshan nyid sogs //
NK073(pu)001:525: gang nas 'bebs kyang rgyas par bya //
NK073(pu)001:526: thams cad 'jigs med dam tshig dang //
NK073(pu)001:527: shes pa'i dam tshig ldan par bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:528: thams cad ma lus don 'byung ba //
NK073(pu)001:529: tshig gis mtshon las gud na med //
NK073(pu)001:530: sgra nyid don gyi dngos po min //
NK073(pu)001:531: don nyid sgra las gud na med //
NK073(pu)001:532: ming tshig sgra la ma brten par //
NK073(pu)001:533: blo yi gting du go bar byos //
NK073(pu)001:534: gsum bzhi lus don brjod bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:535: sngags mchog bla na med pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:536: mtshan ma kun tu mi rtog par //
NK073(pu)001:537: mnyam pa'i ngang du thams cad shes //
NK073(pu)001:538: kun kyang mnyam pa nyid yin pas //
NK073(pu)001:540: so so'i lta ba brjod mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:541: dag cing blang bar bya ba min //
NK073(pu)001:542: spyir ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK073(pu)001:543: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:544: so sor 'dzin rtog bag chags kyi //
NK073(pu)001:546: cir yang med la cir yang snang //
NK073(pu)001:547: byang chub snying po gzhi las gol //
NK073(pu)001:548: bden mi ma grol bcings pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:549: dus dgras 'joms bslus mi rtag dang //
NK073(pu)001:550: 'phags lam bral dgos btson rar chud //
NK073(pu)001:552: de bas mnyam nyid ma rtogs pas //
NK073(pu)001:554: dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing //
NK073(pu)001:555: dge dang mi dge mi mnyam pa //
NK073(pu)001:556: lha dang mi yi skye gnas te //
NK073(pu)001:558: mnyam pa'i don nyid ma rtogs shing //
NK073(pu)001:559: tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:560: rim par so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK073(pu)001:561: gzugs sogs kun la bdag tu rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:562: 'di nas tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK073(pu)001:563: mnyam dang gzugs med ma rtogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:564: ming bzhi med par mi shes te //
NK073(pu)001:565: skye mched bzhi la gnas 'gyur ba //
NK073(pu)001:566: srid pa'i rtse mo'i sa ru skye //
NK073(pu)001:567: rtag chad gnyis kar gang gis blo zhen pa //
NK073(pu)001:568: don gyi snying po nyid las gol bar gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:569: sa dgu dag pa'i ye shes ni //
NK073(pu)001:570: sa dgu mi spangs ngang du bcom //
NK073(pu)001:571: gnyis med ma rtogs thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:572: bden bzhi'i dngos po yod lta zhing //
NK073(pu)001:573: spong dang mi spong byed 'gyur na //
NK073(pu)001:574: 'di ni nyan thos sa pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:575: las dang nyon mongs thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:576: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK073(pu)001:578: 'di ni rang sangs rgyas kyi sa //
NK073(pu)001:579: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK073(pu)001:580: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:581: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK073(pu)001:582: 'di ni byang chub sa pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:583: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK073(pu)001:584: don dam du ni dbyer med do //
NK073(pu)001:585: kun rdzob tsam du thams cad la /
NK073(pu)001:586: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:587: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK073(pu)001:588: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK073(pu)001:589: kun rdzob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK073(pu)001:590: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK073(pu)001:591: thabs kyi lta spyod chen po ni //
NK073(pu)001:592: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK073(pu)001:593: don dam du ni dkor bdun no //
NK073(pu)001:594: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK073(pu)001:595: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:596: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:597: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:598: mnyam nyid ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:599: thabs kyi phyag rgya chen por rten //
NK073(pu)001:600: thabs dang shes rab rnam par dag /
NK073(pu)001:601: thams cad dag ces bya ba yang //
NK073(pu)001:602: dngos po bsal dag ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:603: snang spyod nyid nas rnam par dag /
NK073(pu)001:604: de phyir kun rdzob rdzun mi lta //
NK073(pu)001:605: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK073(pu)001:606: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK073(pu)001:607: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK073(pu)001:608: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK073(pu)001:609: lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong bas //
NK073(pu)001:610: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK073(pu)001:611: byin rlabs rdo rje'i dbyings sprul pas //
NK073(pu)001:612: blang dor byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:613: de ltar dngos brtag dmigs phyes nas //
NK073(pu)001:614: ma nor don gyi grub mtha' ni //
NK073(pu)001:615: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK073(pu)001:616: 'jig rten lta ba thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:617: ye shes chen pos rab brtag na //
NK073(pu)001:618: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:619: rang bzhin dbyings las nyams pa med //
NK073(pu)001:620: nyams pa'i don ni ji lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:621: mnyam nyid rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK073(pu)001:623: nyams dang rtog pa gang yang med //
NK073(pu)001:624: byang chub sems zhes brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:626: rtog med rang rig kho na tsam //
NK073(pu)001:627: dus gsum sangs rgyas sems la gnas //
NK073(pu)001:628: byang chub sems rnams thams cad ni //
NK073(pu)001:629: shin tu brtag dka' gting zab pas //
NK073(pu)001:630: ma dmigs mi dmigs dmigs su med //
NK073(pu)001:631: sems nyid de ni ci lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:632: byang chub de ni sems yin te //
NK073(pu)001:633: sems dang byang chub dbyer med pas //
NK073(pu)001:634: sems can ma lus thams cad dang //
NK073(pu)001:635: dus gsum chos rnams thams cad yin //
NK073(pu)001:636: yod las btsal na sgro btags te //
NK073(pu)001:637: sgros btags brgyad du ltung bar 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:638: med las btsal na bskur btab ste //
NK073(pu)001:639: skur btab bcu yi gnas su lhung //
NK073(pu)001:640: yod med gnyis la btsal byas na //
NK073(pu)001:641: de snyed lung du ma bstan 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:642: de phyir nam mkha' yod med ces //
NK073(pu)001:643: blun po rnams ni rtsod par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:644: mkhas pas nam mkha' rang bzhin las //
NK073(pu)001:646: sems nyid yod med kun ngo bo //
NK073(pu)001:647: sgra tsam brjod du rung mod kyi //
NK073(pu)001:648: ngo bo 'di zhes bstan dka' la //
NK073(pu)001:649: yod dang med ces ci byar yod //
NK073(pu)001:650: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK073(pu)001:651: de min lta ba bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:652: gnyis med mnyam dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK073(pu)001:653: bdag nyid lhun grub chos dbyings dag /
NK073(pu)001:654: byang chub chos nyid stoong bsam 'das //
NK073(pu)001:655: de bzhin nyid dang skye 'gags med //
NK073(pu)001:656: mtha' bral 'das dang grol sogs su //
NK073(pu)001:657: bla dwags tsam du brjod pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:658: ye nas tshig dngos tshig lam chad //
NK073(pu)001:659: sems nyid de kun rang bzhin la //
NK073(pu)001:660: de dag sgra brjod bsnyad ci yod //
NK073(pu)001:661: bstan brtag dka' bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:663: ye shes can gyi spyod yul de //
NK073(pu)001:664: kun dang thun mong de ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:665: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul de //
NK073(pu)001:666: skye bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:667: de phyir blo can rnams kyis brtson //
NK073(pu)001:668: shes pa'i mtshan nyid dngos ming grangs //
NK073(pu)001:669: ngo bo rim pas phye ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:670: snga ma kha cig mngon sum la //
NK073(pu)001:671: drug gam brgyad nyid gnas 'gyur phyir //
NK073(pu)001:672: shes rab dbang drug tshul gnas brjod //
NK073(pu)001:673: nges par ma nor mthong ba yang //
NK073(pu)001:674: ye shes lnga ru gsal ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:675: brgyad kyi ngo bo de nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:676: lnga dang dmigs byed med phyir te //
NK073(pu)001:677: de bas yul med rang gsal ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:678: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis med par //
NK073(pu)001:679: de bzhin nyid du rdo rje'i rigs //
NK073(pu)001:680: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)001:681: dmigs med tshul du rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:682: yangs shing rgya che lhun grub ni //
NK073(pu)001:683: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas dag /
NK073(pu)001:684: bdag rtog nyid kyang dbyings nyid yin //
NK073(pu)001:685: 'di ni rdo rje mnyam yin no //
NK073(pu)001:686: shes dang spyod yul gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)001:687: thams cad ma lus gcig pu'i ngang //
NK073(pu)001:688: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal stong gzugs //
NK073(pu)001:689: lta dang lta bar byar med par //
NK073(pu)001:690: phyogs bcu zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK073(pu)001:691: gang du'ang ma mthong spyan gyi mchog /
NK073(pu)001:692: khyab gsal rang bzhin go ba'i sgra //
NK073(pu)001:693: thos pa med par thos pa'i phul //
NK073(pu)001:694: dwangs pas tshim byed chos nyid dri //
NK073(pu)001:695: snom byed med par tshor ba'i shangs //
NK073(pu)001:696: don bcud nyams su myong ba'i ro //
NK073(pu)001:697: myong ba'i bya byed gnyis med myong //
NK073(pu)001:698: yang dag don la reg pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:699: reg pa kun dngos reg dang bral //
NK073(pu)001:700: chos khams sna tshogs kun mkhyen pa //
NK073(pu)001:701: rang rig rgyal po snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:702: de bas bdag 'dzin rang gsal ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:703: bdag bcas bdag dang bral ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:704: don dang sems can rtog med gsal //
NK073(pu)001:705: rang byung ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NK073(pu)001:706: yang ni rim par don grangs brjod //
NK073(pu)001:707: don dam kun rdzob gnyis med mthong //
NK073(pu)001:708: mngon byas rig pa rtogs goms rim //
NK073(pu)001:709: rnam bzhi lam dang sgom bzhi dang //
NK073(pu)001:710: bsnyen sgrub lam grangs nyams g.yo thob //
NK073(pu)001:711: goms brtan mthar phyin rim par 'phar //
NK073(pu)001:712: mnyam nyid ngang la mi skrag pas //
NK073(pu)001:713: mngon byas nges pa'i shes rab dang //
NK073(pu)001:714: rnam par kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK073(pu)001:715: rang rig snying po ye shes gzigs //
NK073(pu)001:716: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bu lta //
NK073(pu)001:717: tha ga ral pa'i lta ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:718: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong //
NK073(pu)001:719: dbang bsgyur mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK073(pu)001:720: ye shes kun mkhyen lta ba dgu //
NK073(pu)001:721: thos bsam so sor rtog bsgom dang //
NK073(pu)001:722: rnal 'byor rim pa rgyu las skyes //
NK073(pu)001:723: de bas shes rab gsum la 'bad //
NK073(pu)001:724: rgyud don gzungs phyir zin pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:725: dam tshig dam tshig zhes bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:726: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK073(pu)001:727: sdom pa rnam pa bcu gsum dang //
NK073(pu)001:728: spyi yi dam tshig mtha' yas pa //
NK073(pu)001:729: thig le chen po'i ngang du gsal //
NK073(pu)001:730: ci ltar spyad kyang sdom mi 'da' //
NK073(pu)001:731: spyod pa rnam pa gnyis po yang //
NK073(pu)001:732: thig le chen po'i ngang du nges //
NK073(pu)001:733: ci la'ang mi gnas kun la spyod //
NK073(pu)001:734: spyod par byed dang spyad med mthong //
NK073(pu)001:735: bya byed med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK073(pu)001:736: kun la thogs pa med par spyad //
NK073(pu)001:737: bzhi yi las dang gcig po yang //
NK073(pu)001:738: thig le chen po'i ngang du gsal //
NK073(pu)001:739: mchod pa'i rgyan dang longs spyod kun //
NK073(pu)001:740: rig pa byang chub sems chen po //
NK073(pu)001:742: phul ba med par thams cad mnyes //
NK073(pu)001:743: gzhal yas khang dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK073(pu)001:745: sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin //
NK073(pu)001:746: de bas rnam bdun rig pa'i ngang //
NK073(pu)001:747: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:748: rang bzhin ngang gis bdag nyid phyir //
NK073(pu)001:749: dbang lnga ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:750: bco brgyad rang rig cho 'phrul snang //
NK073(pu)001:751: e ma'o ma bsgrub grub chen po //
NK073(pu)001:752: grub pa chen po ye shes che //
NK073(pu)001:753: don du gnyer ba'i rnam grangs kun //
NK073(pu)001:754: rang rig byang chub sems chen po //
NK073(pu)001:755: ting 'dzin lta ba'i bye brag kun //
NK073(pu)001:756: rang rig snang phyir chu bur dang //
NK073(pu)001:757: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin las //
NK073(pu)001:758: rang rig ye shes nyid las min //
NK073(pu)001:759: sngags dang phyag rgya sems nyid phyir //
NK073(pu)001:760: brag cha chu zla 'drar shes nas //
NK073(pu)001:761: bcings brjod las nyid mya ngan 'das //
NK073(pu)001:762: de bas bya byed mnyam nyid rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:763: lta ba lta ba gtsor brjod mod //
NK073(pu)001:764: don du shes rab kun mnyam nyid //
NK073(pu)001:765: ded dpon rin chen ji bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:766: gtod mtha'i bye brag 'dir shes dgongs //
NK073(pu)001:767: shes rab rtogs pas gnyer chub tshe //
NK073(pu)001:768: bdag dang gzhan phyir bya ba rnams //
NK073(pu)001:769: shes pa zhi la kun kyang spyod //
NK073(pu)001:770: thos bsam bcu spyod don du gnyer //
NK073(pu)001:771: 'di yang rgyal po'i sa khams yang //
NK073(pu)001:772: stobs can rtsal skyed drag zhan dang //
NK073(pu)001:773: mkha' yul che chung ji lta ba //
NK073(pu)001:774: gzhi gcig stobs kyis khyad par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:775: ye nas dbyings su ro gcig pas //
NK073(pu)001:776: de la'ang nga dang bdag ma rtog /
NK073(pu)001:777: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa la //
NK073(pu)001:778: gtsang dang dme ba'i blo ma byed //
NK073(pu)001:779: thams cad bde gshegs snying po can //
NK073(pu)001:780: rkyen gyi rdul gyis ga la 'gos //
NK073(pu)001:781: shes rab mchog gis de ltar rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:782: ma lus kun 'dus dbyings su byos //
NK073(pu)001:783: de bas shes par bya ba rnams //
NK073(pu)001:784: dam tshig sdom pa'i ngo bor byed //
NK073(pu)001:785: bdag dang gzhan phyir gtsor byed kyis //
NK073(pu)001:786: dang po'i sdom pa kun kyang slob //
NK073(pu)001:787: shes rab chen po'i sbyin sreg gis //
NK073(pu)001:788: srid gsum sreg pa'i me yin te //
NK073(pu)001:789: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK073(pu)001:790: kun kyang chos nyid ngang du bsgral //
NK073(pu)001:791: gtog mthar lam gnyer spros gcod cing //
NK073(pu)001:792: grub pa bgrong dang 'jug pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:793: bdag dang gzhan phyir dam 'cha' bas //
NK073(pu)001:794: bdag nyid la'ang gzhan don rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:795: de bas byas par mi mtshungs te //
NK073(pu)001:796: lam kun skabs la shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:797: gang gis 'di ltar mthong rtogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:798: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ste //
NK073(pu)001:799: chu sprin phyag rgya ci lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:800: dang po don rtogs mtha' mi gtong //
NK073(pu)001:801: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK073(pu)001:802: kun nas nyon mongs spyod pa'ang grol //
NK073(pu)001:803: thun mong lam gnyis de bzhin pas //
NK073(pu)001:804: rnam smin gnyis med tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:805: gang gis de ltar rtogs 'gyur ba //
NK073(pu)001:806: sgro skur gsum las rab grol te //
NK073(pu)001:808: de bas bdag gzhan chos don rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:809: rgya che zab yangs shes rab myur //
NK073(pu)001:810: zab pa'i don rtogs mi ldog bde //
NK073(pu)001:811: dad dang bdag med yangs pa bde //
NK073(pu)001:812: brtson pas rtogs pa myur byed na //
NK073(pu)001:813: dbang thob bden mthong mtshan mthong zhing //
NK073(pu)001:814: rtsa ba'i drod las yan lag kun //
NK073(pu)001:815: shugs kyis 'byung bar the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:816: de las mtshan ma 'byung ba ni //
NK073(pu)001:817: stobs kyis rtogs pa'i klungs ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:819: 'khrul pa'i khams la skyo ba med //
NK073(pu)001:820: grub pa'i gnas na smon med de //
NK073(pu)001:821: 'dod pa'i longs spyod mnyam par sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:822: sdug bsngal nyon mongs bzod chen deng //
NK073(pu)001:823: las rnams gang la khur mi blta //
NK073(pu)001:825: tha mal spyod las lhag par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:826: spyod pa rgyun gyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:827: mdo smros tha dad brjod mi long //
NK073(pu)001:828: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK073(pu)001:829: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK073(pu)001:830: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral bar //
NK073(pu)001:831: rang gsal gsum bral mi 'gul bas //
NK073(pu)001:832: nges par deng du gang byas pa //
NK073(pu)001:833: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK073(pu)001:834: 'on kyang sa dang sa yi rim //
NK073(pu)001:835: dbang po dwangs ma'i spyod yul ba //
NK073(pu)001:836: nye ring drung zhing stobs 'phel bas //
NK073(pu)001:838: gsal ba'i bye brag rim par 'gro //
NK073(pu)001:839: de bas skabs mi brjod dngos gcig /
NK073(pu)001:840: gong gi don ltar ma rtogs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:841: blo ngan mnyam pa'i khungs phyung nas //
NK073(pu)001:842: ma rtogs le lo snyoms las byas //
NK073(pu)001:844: sems kyis mnyam pa ma rtogs na //
NK073(pu)001:845: tshig gis mnyam pas sangs mi rgya //
NK073(pu)001:846: de bas don tshig ldan par byos //
NK073(pu)001:848: spyan bzang lam zhugs ji bzhin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:850: don du mi 'gyur phyir na brlag /
NK073(pu)001:851: de bas don dam 'grus par bgyis //
NK073(pu)001:852: de ltar don mthong gang zhig gis //
NK073(pu)001:853: gzhan du mi bsal 'dris bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:854: skyes bu dam pa mchog 'dod pas //
NK073(pu)001:855: de la rtag 'grus gsal bar gyis //
NK073(pu)001:856: lam shes lam du 'jug bzhin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:858: rang gnas mthong ba'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:860: // bdag nyid ngang chen rtogs pas mo //
NK073(pu)001:861: de rjes goms byed bshad par bya //
NK073(pu)001:862: snga ma snga ma gang dang gang //
NK073(pu)001:863: phyi ma phyi ma thabs dang rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:864: de bzhin phyi ma phyi ma gang //
NK073(pu)001:865: snga ma snga ma las byung 'bras //
NK073(pu)001:867: srid pa'i 'khor lo tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:868: dbang po brtson 'grus bzang ngan kyang //
NK073(pu)001:869: rnam par dbye ba'i lus gnyis bstan //
NK073(pu)001:870: srid par rdzogs par smin tshul du //
NK073(pu)001:871: lhag par gding ldan skyes bu yis //
NK073(pu)001:872: bsgom pa rnam bzhi zung ldan par //
NK073(pu)001:873: gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed //
NK073(pu)001:874: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK073(pu)001:875: sgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:876: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK073(pu)001:877: de ni kun tu snang gi ngang //
NK073(pu)001:878: de ni rgyu yi rim par ldan //
NK073(pu)001:879: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:880: ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:881: ye shes lnga ru gsal ba nyid //
NK073(pu)001:882: thugs kyi phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK073(pu)001:883: mnyam las mnyam par sbyar ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:884: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK073(pu)001:886: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK073(pu)001:887: yang na dam tshig 'di lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:888: ji ltar spyad kyang sdom mi 'da' //
NK073(pu)001:889: byed spyod tshogs chen gnyis su 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:891: ma nyams de yi dbyings su gnas //
NK073(pu)001:892: shes rab mchog gis rtag tu spyad //
NK073(pu)001:893: dbyings nyid la ni dbyings spyod phyir //
NK073(pu)001:894: dbyings nyid mchog gi gnas la spyod //
NK073(pu)001:895: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NK073(pu)001:896: rtog pa'i ye shes yid bzhin gter //
NK073(pu)001:897: thams cad la yang me long bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:898: bltas kyang gzugs snang mi snang ngo //
NK073(pu)001:899: shes rgyud ci yin gang gis ngo shes shing //
NK073(pu)001:900: bya byed las 'phags ci 'drar 'dug byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:901: gang zhig blo la spyod pa byang chub thob //
NK073(pu)001:902: rnam par dag pa'i g.yung drung sangs rgyas la //
NK073(pu)001:903: thams cad ye nas mnyam par rnam dag cing //
NK073(pu)001:904: mi rtog sa ler gnas la rtogs pa med //
NK073(pu)001:905: bsnyad du med pa sna tshogs 'byung ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:906: bdag med bdag chen thams cad 'byung ba'i gter //
NK073(pu)001:907: ma bkag pa la rgyud cing 'byung med pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:908: rnam rtog nyid na ye shes rang bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:909: rnam pa gsum du snang zhing stong nyid pas //
NK073(pu)001:910: rnam rtog mi skye ye shes brjod du med //
NK073(pu)001:911: thams cad sems kyi ngang ste sems zhes gdags su med //
NK073(pu)001:912: ma bcos lhun gnas ye nas byang chub cing //
NK073(pu)001:913: thob tu med pas ye nas bder gshegs yin //
NK073(pu)001:914: nam mkhar gzung bas sprin gyis khebs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:915: nam mkha' med par gang gis shes pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:916: sprin zhig 'byung zhing khebs par mi srid bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:917: bsgom pa'i sems kyang de ltar blta bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:918: ma bcos lhun gnas ci bzhin ngang gzhag dang //
NK073(pu)001:919: rgyu 'bras lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:920: de bzhin nyid gnas la bcas na //
NK073(pu)001:921: nyon mongs sdug bsngal mi 'byung ste //
NK073(pu)001:922: rtag tu bde gnas byang chub cing //
NK073(pu)001:923: mtshan dang dpe byad kun dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:924: srid pa'i rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:925: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru gzhag /
NK073(pu)001:926: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK073(pu)001:927: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:928: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK073(pu)001:929: skye ba rim gsum gnyis med do //
NK073(pu)001:930: dang po las la ston byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:931: de bzhin nyid du goms bya ba'ang //
NK073(pu)001:932: sngon dgos thabs dang ngo bor dang //
NK073(pu)001:933: mi mthun bcos nyams spyod dam tshig /
NK073(pu)001:934: drod rtogs mtshan yon 'da' ka ma //
NK073(pu)001:936: skyes bu seng ge bzhin rgyu bas //
NK073(pu)001:937: sngon du ri mo rim par rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:938: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK073(pu)001:939: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK073(pu)001:940: byang chub sems dang snying rje lnga //
NK073(pu)001:941: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs bya //
NK073(pu)001:942: de nas ma yi sems ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:943: gnas drug thar par 'god dam bcas //
NK073(pu)001:944: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi sngon song bas //
NK073(pu)001:945: yid 'ong skyon med sa btsal bslang //
NK073(pu)001:946: ran byas byi dor ldan byas bsrung //
NK073(pu)001:947: si sar stan dang ldan par byas //
NK073(pu)001:948: bar chad sel zhing lam rdzogs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:949: tshogs dang sbyin sreg dpung tshogs 'bar //
NK073(pu)001:950: phyi nang 'brel chags thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:951: gzhan phyir dur rkun sems kyis dor //
NK073(pu)001:952: pha dang ting 'dzin rkyen bsdus la //
NK073(pu)001:953: bar chad bsrung bar sngon rdzogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:954: longs spyod rig ma'ang ldan byas la //
NK073(pu)001:956: thun mong spyi yi sngon rdzogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:957: mchod bstod nye ba'i gzugs brnyan bzhugs //
NK073(pu)001:958: yan lag brgyad pa'i tshul gzung la //
NK073(pu)001:960: dag pa rnam gsum ma nor zhing //
NK073(pu)001:961: rang rig rgyal por goms pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:962: byang chub mchog nyid rnyed par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:963: de phyir mthong rjes de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:964: snying rje 'byung ba'i gzhi ru gzhag /
NK073(pu)001:965: go rim 'byung ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:966: gang dag skal ldan cung dman pas //
NK073(pu)001:967: gzhan sel phyir dang don gnyer phyir //
NK073(pu)001:968: 'jug pa'ang snga ma gnyis don du //
NK073(pu)001:970: ye shes sgron ma'i mda' 'phang nas //
NK073(pu)001:971: gti mug mun pa rnam bsal te //
NK073(pu)001:972: rang bzhin 'od gsal bde ba'i mchog /
NK073(pu)001:973: mdor na sgrib tsog mun snang tshul //
NK073(pu)001:974: chos dbyings mkha' dkyil yangs pa la //
NK073(pu)001:975: shes rab myur du don go ba //
NK073(pu)001:977: byang chub sems mchog a rab bde //
NK073(pu)001:978: mun snang tug rtsi'i tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:979: rtogs pa'i dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK073(pu)001:980: don du gnyer ba gang dag kun //
NK073(pu)001:983: rgya mtsho'i mjing gi pha bong ltar //
NK073(pu)001:984: bskal par lam la btsal byas kyang //
NK073(pu)001:985: don med snying po skams pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:986: de phyir lhag ma cha bsnyams pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:987: bde ldan brod pa chos bdun tshul //
NK073(pu)001:988: ldan bya rje btsun rnam snang bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:990: de yang gdams ngag shes rab kyis //
NK073(pu)001:991: stobs kyis bzhag pa goms par byed //
NK073(pu)001:992: sngon brjod bu de dben ba'i sar //
NK073(pu)001:993: rin chen lhab lhub longs spyod kyis //
NK073(pu)001:994: mnyes bya bu de sa ru bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:995: bgegs skrod sbubs mchus zhib bur bstim //
NK073(pu)001:997: shin tu mi dmigs dbyings su bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:998: phyi ma'ang spyi blugs mthong rjes bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:999: bdag dang bdag gir gzhan rnams ni //
NK073(pu)001:1000: shin tu mi dmigs dbyings su bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1001: rang rig nyid la gnas pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:1002: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ste //
NK073(pu)001:1003: thams cad de bzhin nyid du sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1004: gnyis med dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK073(pu)001:1005: rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1006: ma lus de bzhin nyid du sdud //
NK073(pu)001:1007: sdud dang mi sdud gnyis ka min //
NK073(pu)001:1008: yang dag kho na nyid du'o //
NK073(pu)001:1009: bsgom bya sgom byed ma skyes nas //
NK073(pu)001:1010: chos nyid bsgom par bya ba'am med //
NK073(pu)001:1011: don dam bsgom par bya med pas //
NK073(pu)001:1012: gang la mi 'jug zhugs pa'i mchog /
NK073(pu)001:1013: bsam bya bsam par mi bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:1014: mi bsam par yang mi bsam mo //
NK073(pu)001:1015: gang la rnam par mi dmigs pa //
NK073(pu)001:1016: de nyid rang nyid mnyam nyid do //
NK073(pu)001:1017: byang chub sems kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1018: shin tu mi dmigs brtag dka' bas //
NK073(pu)001:1019: yangs la rgya che gting zab pas //
NK073(pu)001:1020: shes rab zab pas rtogs 'gyur te //
NK073(pu)001:1023: shin tu brtag dka' mi dmigs pas //
NK073(pu)001:1024: mtha' dang dbus kyang brtag tu med //
NK073(pu)001:1025: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1026: dmigs med tshul du der snang ngo //
NK073(pu)001:1027: dbyings dang dbyings kyi ye shes kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1028: rang rig kho na tsam du zad //
NK073(pu)001:1029: gang zhig dmigs ni 'jug pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:1031: 'jug med sangs rgyas yin par ni //
NK073(pu)001:1032: dbang po nyid du kun gyis gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:1033: nges par bsam zhing dmigs yod na //
NK073(pu)001:1035: de bzhin nyid de mi mthong ste //
NK073(pu)001:1037: rnal 'byor mnyam pa de bzhin pas //
NK073(pu)001:1038: ngo bo bzhin du grangs 'dzug ci //
NK073(pu)001:1039: nges tshig rna bar 'byung ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:1040: de bas kun la 'byor bar gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1041: chen po dman pas thabs bsal ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:1042: ma skyes de bzhin nyid stong pa //
NK073(pu)001:1043: gdod stong stong pa'i tha snyad bral //
NK073(pu)001:1044: spros pa brgyad bral 'dod ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:1045: gang gis rang gi mtha' dri ma //
NK073(pu)001:1046: med pas de bzhin dag pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1047: rnal 'byor mtshan med de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1048: gnyis med lhun mnyam de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1049: grangs bzhi'i tha ma rim pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1050: byin rlabs yon tan ngo bos bla //
NK073(pu)001:1051: bla ma'ang skabs ming mnyam nyid dang //
NK073(pu)001:1052: lhun grub mtha' bral tha snyad med //
NK073(pu)001:1053: stong chen ma skyed chos dbyings sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1054: yon tan cha re yod bar zad //
NK073(pu)001:1055: de re'ang skabs kyi ngo bo dang //
NK073(pu)001:1056: ming don nges tshig yod pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1057: gtan tshig yan lag tu ldan pa //
NK073(pu)001:1059: lhag pa'i don mchog gang yin pa //
NK073(pu)001:1060: don rnams nyid na dngos med pas //
NK073(pu)001:1061: rtogs pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK073(pu)001:1062: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK073(pu)001:1063: de nyid rang gsal mi g.yo ba //
NK073(pu)001:1064: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK073(pu)001:1065: thams cad shes rab dbyings nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:1066: dbyings la dbyings ni rnam par sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1067: shes rab dbyings nyid sbyor ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:1068: byang chub rdo rje thig le yin //
NK073(pu)001:1069: de yang so sor rtog bsgom dang //
NK073(pu)001:1070: mi dmigs shin tu mi dmigs dang //
NK073(pu)001:1071: rjes su mi dmigs rim pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1072: mi gnas mi rtog rlom sems med //
NK073(pu)001:1073: rang bzhin ngang gis bdag med pas //
NK073(pu)001:1074: bya byed gnyid ka mi dmigs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1075: mkha' ltar 'du byed kun bral ba //
NK073(pu)001:1076: bsam med 'dug la bsgom zhes brjod //
NK073(pu)001:1077: 'du shes gang du'ang ma zhugs na //
NK073(pu)001:1079: de lta de ltar mnyam bzhag tshe //
NK073(pu)001:1080: gnas dang spyod lam sgrib pa rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1081: nor bar zin nas mi 'phrog par //
NK073(pu)001:1082: bya phyir mdo tsam brjod par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1083: dmigs pa brjed dang bying rgod drug /
NK073(pu)001:1084: rtsol dang mi rtsol byed pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1085: dgos dang log pa bcu gcig dang //
NK073(pu)001:1086: thun mong bdun te bco brgyad do //
NK073(pu)001:1087: de bzhin g.yeng ba rnam drug ste //
NK073(pu)001:1088: ngo bos g.yeng ba rnam shes lnga //
NK073(pu)001:1089: phyi rol yul lngar 'phros pa'i g.yeng //
NK073(pu)001:1090: bying rgod ro myong nang yin te //
NK073(pu)001:1091: gzhan phyir dge sbyor mtshan ma'o //
NK073(pu)001:1092: snyoms 'jug gzhan nam theg pa gzhan //
NK073(pu)001:1093: de yi lugs la sems 'phro yid //
NK073(pu)001:1095: gnas ngan len par the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1097: 'gog dang ther zug phyal ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1098: ched du gsum 'chos yid la byed //
NK073(pu)001:1099: myong dang 'du shes gnas dmigs dang //
NK073(pu)001:1100: sdud dang mngon byed re ba mang //
NK073(pu)001:1101: sgrib pa lnga bcu rtsa yan lag /
NK073(pu)001:1102: 'jig rten dang po bsam gtan bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:1103: snyoms 'jug bzhir gol sa dgu ste //
NK073(pu)001:1104: ther zug chad pa phyin ci log /
NK073(pu)001:1105: bya ba mang la rkyen 'byung zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1106: ngang thung 'khrug dang dung gshang thos //
NK073(pu)001:1107: 'khor zhing kha dog mthong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1108: khams las gyur pa'i cha yang shes //
NK073(pu)001:1110: longs spyod tshe na'ang rnal 'byor bral //
NK073(pu)001:1111: ye'u tse tur rkun nya glang gnyid //
NK073(pu)001:1112: bskam chags tshogs sems spre'u spyod skyon //
NK073(pu)001:1113: de ltar shes pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK073(pu)001:1114: spong ba'i 'du byed brgyad bsten pa //
NK073(pu)001:1115: so sor cung zad blta byas pa'am //
NK073(pu)001:1116: yang na rang byung rang zhir bya //
NK073(pu)001:1117: ji ltar byis pa shed ma bye //
NK073(pu)001:1118: bya byed mang pos g.yeng bar gnas //
NK073(pu)001:1119: bya byed mang po bdag med par //
NK073(pu)001:1120: ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:1121: mtshan ma mnyam pa'i dbyings su gnon //
NK073(pu)001:1122: dgag dang sgrub pa ga la yin //
NK073(pu)001:1123: cung zad khams kyi cha nyams pa //
NK073(pu)001:1124: mi gsal mthong dang mi 'jug sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1125: zin nas spyod lam dga' rten dang //
NK073(pu)001:1126: mthun pa'i cho gas gso bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1127: spyod lam rnal du ma 'byor ba //
NK073(pu)001:1128: so 'thas chod nas dor bar bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:1129: dran pa'i thag bas bsdams byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1130: rnam par kun tu nyams mi bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:1131: de ltar nogs brtson yun ring bar //
NK073(pu)001:1133: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa //
NK073(pu)001:1134: mu lngas yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1135: gang dag gzar sor chur gnas tshe //
NK073(pu)001:1136: kun brtag goms pa'i rdza mkhan de //
NK073(pu)001:1137: mi sdod skyo bas 'gro bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:1138: de tshe mgo la me 'bar bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1139: cung zad yod la de dag nyung //
NK073(pu)001:1141: de goms ched du byed sogs na //
NK073(pu)001:1142: btang snyoms dang po blang bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1143: ri bo lta bur mi 'gul la //
NK073(pu)001:1144: thun rkyang nus nas sun mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1145: ro myong dor nas de mthar phyin //
NK073(pu)001:1146: shugs snang mthong la dga' brod med //
NK073(pu)001:1148: khams dang 'chor rgyu brtag gos dor //
NK073(pu)001:1149: shin tu yun ring brtson pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1151: bdag dang gzhan phyir bya ba kun //
NK073(pu)001:1152: slob g.yon nas bzung lnga yi bar //
NK073(pu)001:1153: rnam par rtog med tshul gyis ni //
NK073(pu)001:1154: thams cad kun la chags med rol //
NK073(pu)001:1155: spyod dgu dor ba'i gcig cha'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1156: mi dmigs mthun pa'i spyod ces bya //
NK073(pu)001:1159: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK073(pu)001:1160: gnas pa nyid na'ang gnas pa med //
NK073(pu)001:1161: longs spyod med las thams cad spyod //
NK073(pu)001:1162: spyod pa nyid na spyod med pa //
NK073(pu)001:1163: nyams pa med spyod chags mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1165: bdag phyir kun la mi dmigs pa //
NK073(pu)001:1166: rnal 'byor myur thob the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1168: de ltar spyod pas chos nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:1169: byin rlabs sgrol bas gcig shos te //
NK073(pu)001:1170: gang yang gzhan phyir sems dpas rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:1171: gzhung las grags pa'i spyod pa rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1172: skye bo kun gyis spyad gsungs pa //
NK073(pu)001:1173: mos slob ci smos rkyen mthong na //
NK073(pu)001:1174: de dag shes goms bzhi la spyod //
NK073(pu)001:1175: shes 'jug kun kyang gzhan don du //
NK073(pu)001:1176: las bzhi spyod cing bsgrub dbang tshe //
NK073(pu)001:1177: lam kun skad cig chas bsgom na //
NK073(pu)001:1178: spros pa'i 'khor lo mos bsgoms byed //
NK073(pu)001:1179: rang bzhin phabs rdzogs mchod bsnyen nas //
NK073(pu)001:1180: nus pa'i byin ldan rdzogs par byed //
NK073(pu)001:1181: de tshe sdom pa thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:1182: mos slob mi gtong bsrung mod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1183: khyad par ting 'dzin dam tshig ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1184: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:1185: logs na yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:1186: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK073(pu)001:1187: mi gtong phyir yang dam zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:1188: gzungs su gyur pas dam zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:1189: sngar ldan de yang 'dir goms byed //
NK073(pu)001:1190: de bas rang sems rtogs byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1191: le lo g.yeng ba yongs spangs la //
NK073(pu)001:1192: nga dang bdag med mnyam par bsrung //
NK073(pu)001:1193: de bzhin nyid las 'da' mi byed //
NK073(pu)001:1194: de bzhin nyid ldan dam pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:1196: snga ma snga ma rdzogs byas pa //
NK073(pu)001:1197: gong ma gong ma rgyud ldan pa //
NK073(pu)001:1198: yongs su 'phar gyi mngon spyod min //
NK073(pu)001:1199: 'phar bas spyod kun mngon du rgyu //
NK073(pu)001:1200: de bas so so'i lta gzhi la //
NK073(pu)001:1201: spyod sogs khyad par mkha' yul 'dra //
NK073(pu)001:1202: zhing khams dbang pos sa khams bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1203: stobs ni stobs can rtsal skyid 'dra //
NK073(pu)001:1204: de ltar bya byed med bsrings nas //
NK073(pu)001:1205: lus ngag sems la drod 'byung ste //
NK073(pu)001:1206: bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1207: 'gyu ba'i dbugs la dbang thob dang //
NK073(pu)001:1208: don la rnal du phebs pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:1209: nges par drod gsum myong ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:1210: gzhan du phyi rol rdul phran dang //
NK073(pu)001:1211: zla tshes la sogs mtshan ma mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1212: rig pa klong du phebs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1215: phyi nang chags bral zhen pa chung //
NK073(pu)001:1216: snga bas dpags pa nyams su 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1217: gzhan yul thugs rjes sems 'phrogs dang //
NK073(pu)001:1218: chos brgyad mnyam snyoms phal cher 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1219: brod pa bsu zhing zang zing dag /
NK073(pu)001:1220: don du gnyer la brtson par byed //
NK073(pu)001:1222: drod rtags mthong ba'i brod tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1223: shin tu lam la brtson par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1224: de phyir 'di yi rjes su bstan //
NK073(pu)001:1225: de yang g.yo thob brtan rim gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1227: khru ljo smin pa'i rigs de la //
NK073(pu)001:1228: pha mas khyim thabs ltas bstan na //
NK073(pu)001:1229: phyi ma'ang lam gyi stobs cha la //
NK073(pu)001:1231: de la snga ma phyi nang ste //
NK073(pu)001:1232: phyi rol zad par skyed mched dngos //
NK073(pu)001:1234: nang du bzod thob bye brag dang //
NK073(pu)001:1235: chu lnga rgyun la bgas kyis bcad //
NK073(pu)001:1236: mi 'phrogs myos skrag dga' brod med //
NK073(pu)001:1237: shugs snang brgyad po mthong ba'ang 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1238: bco brgyad bdud yul cha yang 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1239: mngon par shes pa rnam par drug /
NK073(pu)001:1240: lam gyi zag pa yod med pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1241: sngon la dmigs pa'i mngon shes dang //
NK073(pu)001:1242: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon shes dang //
NK073(pu)001:1243: bar chad med pa'i mngon shes so //
NK073(pu)001:1244: dmigs pa dga' dang 'phel pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1245: nyi shu rtsa sogs yul khams mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1246: gling grangs mthong thos rim pas phye //
NK073(pu)001:1247: phyi ma stong gsum brgya yul dang //
NK073(pu)001:1248: stong gsum stong sogs yul 'gyur sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1249: stong gsum stong phrag bcu rdul snyed //
NK073(pu)001:1250: grangs med brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul //
NK073(pu)001:1251: de nyid yul 'gyur rgyal ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1252: mnyam bas phye bas lam rdzogs yin //
NK073(pu)001:1253: de yi rgyu yi sems dpa' dang //
NK073(pu)001:1254: skal mnyam phyir na brjod kyi tshul //
NK073(pu)001:1255: shes pa'i khyad par dgongs pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:1256: gzhi yis phye bas rgyu 'bras nges //
NK073(pu)001:1258: chos snang kun brjod gcig char la //
NK073(pu)001:1260: nyams mtha'i bzhi cha 'byung srid do //
NK073(pu)001:1261: rnal 'byor gnas pa'i rmi lam yang //
NK073(pu)001:1262: gcer bur 'byung zhing dri ma dag /
NK073(pu)001:1263: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1264: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:1265: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlobs //
NK073(pu)001:1266: rmi lam mtshan mar bla ma mgon //
NK073(pu)001:1267: snang bas dbang bskur byin rlobs sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1268: lam du 'jug pa lnga byed cing //
NK073(pu)001:1269: bar chad legs nyes brtson lung ston //
NK073(pu)001:1270: de yang bdud dang chas dbye ste //
NK073(pu)001:1271: byin rlobs lung ston lhar snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:1273: bdud dang cha brtag kun tu gces //
NK073(pu)001:1274: bar chad gsal phyir de dag kun //
NK073(pu)001:1275: bla ma nyid las gzhan du min //
NK073(pu)001:1276: de bzhin nyid du mthong goms na //
NK073(pu)001:1277: dge dang mi dge gnyis su med //
NK073(pu)001:1278: rnam rtog mtshan ma yongs mi 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:1279: rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:1280: dge sdig med pa shin tu bde //
NK073(pu)001:1281: bde dang mi bde gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)001:1282: ye shes chags med rnam par dag /
NK073(pu)001:1283: thams cad dbyer med ye shes yin //
NK073(pu)001:1284: sems nyid dang bas a rab bde //
NK073(pu)001:1285: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:1286: gtsang dang dme ba'i blo ma 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:1287: thams cad chos nyid ro gcig pas //
NK073(pu)001:1288: gnyis su med pas shin tu bde //
NK073(pu)001:1289: shes rab che chung ting 'dzin gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1290: thams cad ma nor gzhong lugs bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1291: 'khor ba ma spangs sdug bsngal med //
NK073(pu)001:1292: gnyis med tshim pas a rab bde //
NK073(pu)001:1293: thams cad ma lus gcig pa'i ngang //
NK073(pu)001:1294: lta dang lta ba gnyis ka med //
NK073(pu)001:1295: ye shes sgron ma sbrengs pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:1296: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams ca da mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1297: 'di dang pha rol gnyis med phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1299: yan lag stobs chen ma 'phyongs par //
NK073(pu)001:1300: phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad mnan //
NK073(pu)001:1302: g.yeng bsal stong nyid ngang la 'dug /
NK073(pu)001:1303: dran bas las kyi rgyud bcad de //
NK073(pu)001:1304: 'dod khams lha mi theg chen sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1305: yang na gsang ba'i gser sgrom du //
NK073(pu)001:1306: tshon gang 'od dang zla ba'i h'u //
NK073(pu)001:1307: ring po brtsegs la dmigs thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:1309: snang stong dbyer med rnal 'byor mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:1310: mngon byas lhag pa'i chos sku sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1311: 'bras bu nyid la lam phyir te //
NK073(pu)001:1312: phyogs mthun brjod kyis ris ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:1313: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1315: // chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal te //
NK073(pu)001:1316: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor bshad //
NK073(pu)001:1317: rjes su mthun pa'i lus nyid ni //
NK073(pu)001:1318: yan lag sgo nas shes par gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1319: sngon du stong goms rnal 'byor bas //
NK073(pu)001:1320: khams gsum thugs rjes gzung ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1321: yan lag brgyad sngon bzhin byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1322: ye shes sgyu ma'i snying rje bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1323: bdag nyid dri ma bsal ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1324: stong pa'i mdud pa bshis pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1325: gdul bya sa la dgod pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1326: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rgyu bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1327: rnal 'byor nyid ni gnyer ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1328: bden pa gnyis su mi btang phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1330: 'jug pa'i thun mtshams dus kyis bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:1331: gang gis khams gsum 'das pa'i chos //
NK073(pu)001:1332: thugs rje chen po'i ye shes su //
NK073(pu)001:1333: mthong thos myong reg tshor ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1334: so sor brtag rgyu'am rjes las thob //
NK073(pu)001:1335: de yas ma lus chos so cog /
NK073(pu)001:1336: snying po yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:1337: sgyu ma mig yor sprul pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1338: smig rgyu 'ja' tshon chu zla bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1339: bdag dang 'gro ba ngo bos gcig /
NK073(pu)001:1340: bsal dang brtags pas tha dad phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1341: gcig dang tha snyad gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)001:1342: bya byed bya ba 'gog med par //
NK073(pu)001:1343: mthong ba ma shor tsam du bya //
NK073(pu)001:1344: rjes sam rtog dpyod sngon goms bya //
NK073(pu)001:1345: de bas gnyis goms rgyu goms pas //
NK073(pu)001:1346: dran pa spyi blugs ye shes gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1347: sngon du btang ba gang yang med //
NK073(pu)001:1348: nam mkhas nam mkha' ji bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:1349: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK073(pu)001:1350: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pas //
NK073(pu)001:1351: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:1352: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1353: thams cad thabs kyi mtshan nyid de //
NK073(pu)001:1354: thabs la thabs ni rnam par sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1355: thabs chen thabs las byung ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:1356: de ni byang chub rdo rje mchog /
NK073(pu)001:1357: thams cad du ni ye shes gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1358: ye shes ma yin chos 'ga' yod min pas //
NK073(pu)001:1359: gdung 'dra ma bsgral dus gcig bsgral //
NK073(pu)001:1360: gsod chen snying rje'i rang bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1361: mi 'byed phan rdzogs byams chen po //
NK073(pu)001:1363: tshangs pa'i rgyu bzhin dus gcig rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:1364: mngon par gdung ba de la med //
NK073(pu)001:1365: de phyir rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang //
NK073(pu)001:1366: dus dang rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1367: tshul gyis nyams dang ngo bo dang //
NK073(pu)001:1368: btson ra lta bu brgyad la dmigs //
NK073(pu)001:1369: de yis cig shes bzhi 'byung ba //
NK073(pu)001:1370: pha rol phyin dang mtshungs ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:1371: de dag ngo bo nyid bstan pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1372: rnam grangs bzhin du grangs 'jug ste //
NK073(pu)001:1373: don dang rnal 'byor ngo bo yis //
NK073(pu)001:1375: de la log rtogs sgyu ma ni //
NK073(pu)001:1376: chos dang bdag dang dngos po rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1377: ngo bo yod la sogs brtags pas //
NK073(pu)001:1378: rtog pa sgyu ma'i klong gyur pa //
NK073(pu)001:1379: skyes dang mi bden bslu bar 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1380: rten cing 'brel ba shing rta bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1381: 'jig rten rnam rtogs gzugs brnyan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1382: sgyu ma lta bu rkyen las skyes //
NK073(pu)001:1383: 'phral snang bya ba kun byed kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1384: rtog can rnams la mthun par zad //
NK073(pu)001:1385: gzugs brnyan 'dra phyir brtag pas dben //
NK073(pu)001:1386: de phyir thams cad rdzun pa tsam //
NK073(pu)001:1387: ming la dngos med 'dod pa min //
NK073(pu)001:1388: yang dag nyid du grags so cog /
NK073(pu)001:1389: gnyis snang nyid na gang min pas //
NK073(pu)001:1390: sems phyir cir snang rgyu med 'char //
NK073(pu)001:1391: snang la ngo bo nges med cing //
NK073(pu)001:1392: ci ltar bltas pas snang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1393: snang zhing ther zug chad dang bral //
NK073(pu)001:1394: rgyal ba'i sku yang ma bskyed par //
NK073(pu)001:1395: rig pa ye shes sgyu mar shar //
NK073(pu)001:1396: khams gsum pa'ang de bzhin pa //
NK073(pu)001:1397: thabs chen sgyu ma kun ngo bo //
NK073(pu)001:1398: ye shes la ni ye shes rol //
NK073(pu)001:1399: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog /
NK073(pu)001:1400: rgyal ba mngon 'byung skyob pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1401: byin rlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1402: rgyu rkyen rag lus med pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1403: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po'i mchog /
NK073(pu)001:1405: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1406: yin phyir ngo bo tha dad med //
NK073(pu)001:1407: dman pas snang ba goms byed tsam //
NK073(pu)001:1408: 'gro la skad cig gnyis mi ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1409: rgyud cig ma skyes ma 'gag pas //
NK073(pu)001:1410: gzung 'dzin bral bas rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1411: ye shes sgyu mar mi g.yo gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1412: chu dang zla ba ji bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:1413: mtshungs par gsal ba ngo bor brjod //
NK073(pu)001:1414: sems las ma gtogs chos med phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1415: ye shes sgyu ma gzhan na med //
NK073(pu)001:1416: sgyu ma nyid kyi chags bral ba //
NK073(pu)001:1417: tha snyad tsam du bsgom zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:1418: mi mthun sgrib pa dmigs bzung ba //
NK073(pu)001:1419: rgyu dang ngo bo nyes pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:1420: ma goms pa dang 'grus byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:1421: me dang du ba'i tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:1422: bdag tu 'dzin pa rnam gnyis kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1424: sngon du ji bzhin nyid brtan mod //
NK073(pu)001:1425: mtshams sbyor snying rje g.yung min pas //
NK073(pu)001:1427: rkyen spangs goms pa'i tha mal dkon //
NK073(pu)001:1429: ma nges sa phyogs mkhar bcas mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1430: zad par mthong dang ma nges mdog /
NK073(pu)001:1431: me chu rlung sa'i cha 'khrul bas //
NK073(pu)001:1432: mi gas la mdog mthong khams 'khrugs lta //
NK073(pu)001:1433: sa g.yos mthong ba'ang cha dabye'o //
NK073(pu)001:1434: sprin dang ling tog mun pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1435: gal te gzhung las grags pa'i skyon //
NK073(pu)001:1436: phra rags cha yis sgyu ma'i don //
NK073(pu)001:1437: mi gsal shin tu bul bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:1438: sngon bzhin rtog pa'i nad bcos pa //
NK073(pu)001:1439: shes bzhin so 'thas chod par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1440: de ltar gyur na rkun po'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:1441: ma bsal rang bzhin dwangs bar 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1442: rnam rtog mtshan ma ci skyes kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1443: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1444: chags sdang re dogs mi 'byung ste //
NK073(pu)001:1445: ye shes sgyu ma gzhan du min //
NK073(pu)001:1446: de ltar ma ldan gang dag gis //
NK073(pu)001:1447: tshor nas lo rgyus dpyad pas zhi //
NK073(pu)001:1448: yang na rtog pa'i gnas yul blta //
NK073(pu)001:1449: de mthong mun pa rnam dag sangs //
NK073(pu)001:1450: 'dod min kha dog mthong ba na //
NK073(pu)001:1451: 'byung ba bzhi yi gnyen pos gzhil //
NK073(pu)001:1452: sngon bzhin sngar 'brangs phyis sngon byed //
NK073(pu)001:1453: de ltar rang bzhin rkyen gyis 'gyes //
NK073(pu)001:1454: tshor na thog mtha'i nyes bsams te //
NK073(pu)001:1455: skyo ba bskyed la dor dran cing //
NK073(pu)001:1456: gang du thim na khrus bcag bsang //
NK073(pu)001:1457: brod pas 'jug cing gzengs bstod bya //
NK073(pu)001:1458: de ltar de ltar brtson 'gyur pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1459: skabs su ye shes rnal 'byor nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1460: 'phel pa'ang g.yo thob goms pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1461: brtan mthar 'gro ba'i ngo bo la //
NK073(pu)001:1462: med kyang rab rib chas bdag brjod //
NK073(pu)001:1464: cung zad thun gyi sum char yod //
NK073(pu)001:1465: bzhi cha lnga char de med thob //
NK073(pu)001:1466: thun rkyang bus shing gsal ldan na //
NK073(pu)001:1467: chu rlung dal 'bab tshul bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:1468: sgo rten rdzas ltar rtog rlung gis //
NK073(pu)001:1470: dbang po mngon sum gang byas pa //
NK073(pu)001:1471: bskyed du bya ba med phyir mtha'o //
NK073(pu)001:1472: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK073(pu)001:1473: srid gsum sgyu ma 'dra bar ni //
NK073(pu)001:1474: rdzogs pa byang chub mkhas pas shes //
NK073(pu)001:1475: 'gro ba'i ched du go bgo ste //
NK073(pu)001:1476: 'gro ba de ltar snga nas shes //
NK073(pu)001:1477: log par rtog brtag rnam dag cing //
NK073(pu)001:1478: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1479: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK073(pu)001:1480: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK073(pu)001:1481: rjes su 'jug pa'ang de bzhin shes //
NK073(pu)001:1482: de bzhin nyid dbyings sna tshogs mang po thabs su snang //
NK073(pu)001:1483: thabs nyid sgyu ma mig yor chu zla gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1484: de nyid rang rig ye shes chags med sna tshogs snang //
NK073(pu)001:1485: thabs dang shes rab ldan pas mchog gis gnas gyur ba //
NK073(pu)001:1486: ci ltar spyad kyang zad med gnyis gnyis bsgrib mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1487: shes rab thabs chen mchog la ye nas rol ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:1488: byang chub sems su rgyu gcig pas //
NK073(pu)001:1489: brtse ba'i snying rje chen po 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1490: sangs rgyas sems can gcig rtogs na //
NK073(pu)001:1491: snying rje chen po skye zhes de la bya //
NK073(pu)001:1492: brdal chen blo ni kun tu snang //
NK073(pu)001:1493: thabs chen kun mdzad 'od gsal byams //
NK073(pu)001:1494: thams cad dgyes mdzad dbyings ma gdung //
NK073(pu)001:1495: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:1496: snying rje'i thag pa ma chad par //
NK073(pu)001:1497: nyon mongs lam la grol byed cing //
NK073(pu)001:1498: byams pa dag gis mnyes par gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1499: de bzhin 'khor ba'i btson ra la //
NK073(pu)001:1500: snying rje'i zhags pa cher brkyang nas //
NK073(pu)001:1502: snying rje chen por skyo ma byed //
NK073(pu)001:1503: de bzhin skye bo phal rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:1504: las kyi sgrib pas mi gos shing //
NK073(pu)001:1505: thams cad mngon par sangs rgyas par //
NK073(pu)001:1506: dga' ba dag la 'gyod ma byed //
NK073(pu)001:1507: sems can nga dang bdag med la //
NK073(pu)001:1508: thugs rje gnyis rtogs mi byed de //
NK073(pu)001:1509: bu gcig 'dra bar blo bzhag bya //
NK073(pu)001:1510: thams cad dri ma med par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1511: sngon rdzogs rkyen 'phrad sngon bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1512: rnal 'byor nyid na gzhan don rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:1513: dmigs pa bdun gnyis gdul bya la //
NK073(pu)001:1514: ngo bo las dang phan yon gyi //
NK073(pu)001:1515: phyogs gtad med de thun mong gi //
NK073(pu)001:1516: chen po dag la blar gyur yin //
NK073(pu)001:1517: bdag phyir spyod yul thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:1518: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1519: phyi nang sgrib med gsal ba'i ngang //
NK073(pu)001:1520: ye shes blo brtan shin tu bde //
NK073(pu)001:1521: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:1522: gtsang dang dme ba'i blo ma 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:1523: thams cad ye nas ro gcig pas //
NK073(pu)001:1524: gnyis su med par shin tu bde //
NK073(pu)001:1525: de bas spyad dang mi spang len //
NK073(pu)001:1526: 'dod yon lnga sogs ye shes rol //
NK073(pu)001:1527: thub chen ston pa'i spyod yul ni //
NK073(pu)001:1528: ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1529: chos rnams thams cad dmigs su med //
NK073(pu)001:1530: ye nas sgyu ma cir yang 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1531: zag med zab pas don rtogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:1532: dag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK073(pu)001:1533: ye shes ma bcos kun tu gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1534: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1535: de phyir spyod yul thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:1536: sgyu ma'i ye shes 'da' mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1537: rtsa ba yan lag thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:1538: snga ma bzhin de nus pa 'phel //
NK073(pu)001:1539: de ltar sgyu ma thob goms pas //
NK073(pu)001:1540: 'khor ba'i chos la tshad med pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1543: don med 'dug pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1544: rnam gsum lnga las 'phel bar snang //
NK073(pu)001:1545: nyams rim 'phel ba'i snga rtag ni //
NK073(pu)001:1546: shing bal lta bur yang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1547: lus kyi bzod pa phra thob ring //
NK073(pu)001:1548: khams bde mi bde snyoms pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1549: phal cher yod cing chos brgyad snyoms //
NK073(pu)001:1550: de bas mang dang 'brel la mnyam //
NK073(pu)001:1551: kun kyang lnga las grangs 'phel zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1552: ngo bo gsal ba yun ring ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:1553: lhan cig drung 'dug pha rol gyi //
NK073(pu)001:1554: mngon shes 'phel dang cung zad brtan //
NK073(pu)001:1555: gzhan la'ang shes pa cung zad 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:1556: de bas rnal 'byor brtan par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1557: 'di tshe spyod yul thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:1558: rmi lam du'ang sgyu mar mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1559: snying rje gang bar mthong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1560: byin rlabs dbang bskur mang mthong dang //
NK073(pu)001:1561: bdud kyi spyod yul mtshan mar mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1562: de sogs snang yang chags mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1563: snying rje chen po goms byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1564: rnal 'byor don chen rtogs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1565: dus mtha' med par de ltar bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1566: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK073(pu)001:1567: spyod yul sangs rgyas nyid dang gcig /
NK073(pu)001:1568: sku spyod bsod nams tshogs chen ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1569: de ming ma chags ye shes che //
NK073(pu)001:1570: rnal 'byor phyi ma btsal ba med //
NK073(pu)001:1571: nyid 'od sa bon skyur sgra bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1573: sgyu mar brtan byas las rgyun gcod //
NK073(pu)001:1575: phyi ma'i lan grangs gzhan dag la //
NK073(pu)001:1576: mi ldog dbang bsgyur rigs su nges //
NK073(pu)001:1577: lam 'dir cha rkyen rdzogs bsgrub pa //
NK073(pu)001:1578: mtshan dang dpe byad kun ldan pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1579: dbang phyug chen po'i gnas nyid du //
