NK073(pu)001:1580: mngon du 'byung bar the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1581: ma rtogs le lo snyoms las byas //
NK073(pu)001:1582: don ma grub par ngan song 'gro //
NK073(pu)001:1583: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhin pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1585: // gnyis med ngang la phyag 'tshal nas //
NK073(pu)001:1586: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor bshad //
NK073(pu)001:1587: gang dag rdo rje gsum bsgom pa //
NK073(pu)001:1588: snga ma 'das pa'i lus kyis shes //
NK073(pu)001:1589: spyi yu las sngon rdzogs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1590: 'di nyid sgyu mthar sngon byas shing //
NK073(pu)001:1591: lugs sogs mtshan ma'i phyag rgya gzhan //
NK073(pu)001:1592: de la yan lag brgyad sngon bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1593: 'bras bu yongs su rdzogs bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1594: spros pa rgyu yi thob bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1595: rgyu stong rtog zhen dbang du bya //
NK073(pu)001:1596: rtog pa'i phung sogs gnas 'gyur zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1597: gang dag smin par bya ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1598: phyag rgya rnal 'byor shin tu gces //
NK073(pu)001:1599: de la 'jug thabs rnam gnyis te //
NK073(pu)001:1600: sems sbyang ba dang lhar bskyed pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1601: snga ma gdams ngag shes rab kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1604: rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK073(pu)001:1605: shin tu phra ba a rnams 'phro //
NK073(pu)001:1606: phyogs bcu gang rnams gsal 'gyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:1608: de la 'am yang na thugs yi ge //
NK073(pu)001:1609: de bzhin yang dang yang goms nas //
NK073(pu)001:1610: phyi nang snod bcud h'u du bsdu //
NK073(pu)001:1611: yan lag rnam shes ye shes phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1612: yi ge h'u du shin tu bsdu //
NK073(pu)001:1613: n+ri yi mig gis ltar yod pa //
NK073(pu)001:1614: 'dris nas bdag gzhan don phyir spro //
NK073(pu)001:1615: mchod don rdzogs nas slar bsdus te //
NK073(pu)001:1616: h'u nyid mi dmigs ngang nyid las //
NK073(pu)001:1617: goms par bya ba shin tu gces //
NK073(pu)001:1618: phyi ma tshangs pa srin po'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:1619: rdzogs par bya ba zung du 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1620: tshangs pa'i cha lugs rdzogs bya ba'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1621: gang bsgrub yi ge so so ste //
NK073(pu)001:1622: spyir ni gang bsgom kun dang 'dra //
NK073(pu)001:1623: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du 'du //
NK073(pu)001:1624: 'di ltar de nyid goms bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:1625: sngon du mi dmigs ngang nyid las //
NK073(pu)001:1626: a dkar gsung gi phyag rgya 'bar //
NK073(pu)001:1627: shin tu 'tsher ba gsal bsgom nas //
NK073(pu)001:1628: thams cad ar ni gyur par bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1629: de bzhin nyid du 'dris byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1630: a las ma yi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK073(pu)001:1631: a ma gsal bar 'byor gyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:1632: nyi zla gang ba sgril ba bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1634: rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1635: nyi zla'i gdan la gzhal yas khang //
NK073(pu)001:1636: thams cad bsdus shing 'phro bar bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1637: de dkyil yi ge h'u gnas par //
NK073(pu)001:1638: mthing ka 'tsher la gsal ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:1641: shin tu rdo rje phra bar bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1643: dbyings su yang ni bstim par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1644: de nyid sems dpa'i skur gyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:1645: shin tu phra zhing 'dus par bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1646: de bzhin gnyis med gsal gyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:1647: sku gcig rdo rje dril 'bar bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1648: de bzhin nyid du gyur pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1649: dbu gsum phyag drug nyid du b+he //
NK073(pu)001:1652: phra ba'i gzhal yas gdan dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1653: gnas gcig ye shes sems dpa' bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1654: spyi mgrin tsit+ta gnas gsum du //
NK073(pu)001:1655: byin rlabs rdo rje gsum bsgoom bya //
NK073(pu)001:1656: dbu yi gnas lngar yi ge lnga //
NK073(pu)001:1657: ye shes lnga dbang rdzogs par brgyan //
NK073(pu)001:1658: blo yi shes rab che chung gis //
NK073(pu)001:1659: yang na phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK073(pu)001:1660: chu la nya ldang ci bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:1661: bdag nyid phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK073(pu)001:1662: zhal gsum phyag drug rtag tu bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1663: gzhal yas gdan sogs snga ma bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1664: yan lag dagu'ang de bzhin bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1665: de la shin tu goms par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1667: rim dang cig char sngon bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1668: rdo rje go cha kha dog dang //
NK073(pu)001:1669: gzhal yas la sogs bsgyur de bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1670: thugs kyi rigs la gzhan mos pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1671: 'bru bzhis sbyangs te gdan gnas gcig /
NK073(pu)001:1672: rdo rje rnam gsum rigs su bsgyur //
NK073(pu)001:1673: sku dang yan lag de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:1674: rim pa thob pa'am cig char ba //
NK073(pu)001:1675: brgyad mthar byin phab lhar bskyed la //
NK073(pu)001:1676: mchod pa byin rlabs sku bsgom ste //
NK073(pu)001:1677: yan lag ldan rdzogs mchod bstod bya //
NK073(pu)001:1678: yan lag ma nyams sngags bzlas pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1679: skyon bcu spangs te rnam gsum gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1680: bzlas pa grangs bzhin rdzogs par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1681: spro bsdus bdag dang gzhan don rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:1682: phyi nang gsang ba gang mos su //
NK073(pu)001:1683: bzlas pa tshad du bskyal bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1684: dub na ye shes thig les blta //
NK073(pu)001:1685: nyal bas nang par de nyid las //
NK073(pu)001:1686: h'u sogs bsgyur te sku rdzogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:1687: sngon bzhin brtson pas 'dris par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1688: gzhal yas lha yi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK073(pu)001:1689: sems kyi cho 'phrul rang snang phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1690: lha la dmigs med rig par nyid //
NK073(pu)001:1691: bzhi rdzogs sku de rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:1692: rgyal ba'i rgyal ba rnams kyi sku //
NK073(pu)001:1693: kun tu rin chen lta bu ste //
NK073(pu)001:1694: rdzogs pas rtogs med re ba skong //
NK073(pu)001:1696: phyag rgya yod med grol ma grol //
NK073(pu)001:1697: bdag phyir phyogs med blang dor med //
NK073(pu)001:1698: bying rgod snyoms tsam mnyam gzhag pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1699: mi mthun 'di tshe dmigs gzung ba //
NK073(pu)001:1700: yi ge nas bzung rdzogs pa'i sar //
NK073(pu)001:1701: thun mong kun tu 'byung rags phra //
NK073(pu)001:1703: khyad par rab rim mog mog grib //
NK073(pu)001:1704: gang tshad dmigs la tshad dang tshul //
NK073(pu)001:1705: grangs dang cha lugs mdog dbyibs dang //
NK073(pu)001:1706: kha mdog 'ba' zhig rim par nub //
NK073(pu)001:1707: de ltar 'gyur bar tshor byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1708: 'du byed rlung gis bskyod mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1709: de ltar zin pas de dag kun //
NK073(pu)001:1710: khyad par gsum la sgyu stong 'dug /
NK073(pu)001:1711: rjes las thob pa ma sun 'dug /
NK073(pu)001:1712: drug la ri ltar che gdos bya //
NK073(pu)001:1713: bdun pa dbyibs dang bsre bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1714: brgyad pa spyi min bye brag gnas //
NK073(pu)001:1715: bya min las kun dor byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1716: spyod lam skyon rnams btang bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1717: gnyis la phug mdo rgyag cig la //
NK073(pu)001:1718: goms pa 'phel ba'ang snga ma bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1719: smig rgyu du ba srin me khyer //
NK073(pu)001:1720: mar me nyi ma'i tshul dang sbyar //
NK073(pu)001:1721: gtang snyoms rim dang brtson pa dag /
NK073(pu)001:1722: skabs kyis blang dor nyams las shes //
NK073(pu)001:1723: 'bru bzhis rtag tu mtshams bcad de //
NK073(pu)001:1724: bdag nyid chen po'i tshogs mchod bya //
NK073(pu)001:1725: nang gi sbyin sreg blang bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1726: gzugs sogs thig le'am lha mo drug /
NK073(pu)001:1727: dbang po yul du sbyor ba bya //
NK073(pu)001:1728: zhi khro gang yin skabs kyis bsgyur //
NK073(pu)001:1729: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1730: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK073(pu)001:1731: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:1732: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1734: nyon mongs sdug bsngal tshe na yang //
NK073(pu)001:1735: theg chen phyag rgya mi spangs te //
NK073(pu)001:1736: sngon bzhin sbyor bas myur du 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1737: rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor bar skabs kun //
NK073(pu)001:1738: chos spyod dgu yi spros pa dor //
NK073(pu)001:1739: rgyud la ldan yang blang bya min //
NK073(pu)001:1740: mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin phyir ro //
NK073(pu)001:1741: rdo rje gsum bsgom phyag mi bya //
NK073(pu)001:1742: phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor spyod pa la //
NK073(pu)001:1743: don ldan ma nyams dag byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1745: lha la lha rol bsod nams te //
NK073(pu)001:1746: spyod la ma chags gnyis med pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1748: rkyen dang 'phrad pa'ang mi dor te //
NK073(pu)001:1749: dus min gzhan phyir spros pa len //
NK073(pu)001:1750: gang dang 'tshams pa don rdzogs byed //
NK073(pu)001:1751: bdag phyir thun mong mchog sgrub rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1752: 'di brtan sbyor bar the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1753: gsung gi gzhi ma lhur bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1754: phyag rgya chen po'i rnal 'byor du //
NK073(pu)001:1755: spyod yul thams cad mnyam par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1756: phyi nang gsal ba shin tu 'phel //
NK073(pu)001:1757: thob dang brtan pa'i char gyur te //
NK073(pu)001:1758: longs spyod zhen pa med pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1759: dbang po yul dus goms pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1760: rgyu ba chad dang thun mtshams bral //
NK073(pu)001:1761: drod kyi bye brag kun dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1762: rtags chen goms mthar mtshan ma lnga //
NK073(pu)001:1763: yongs su mthong dang rdo rje gsum //
NK073(pu)001:1764: skye mched mthong dam tshan ma ste //
NK073(pu)001:1765: grub pa dang po rtags zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:1766: dmigs ma rgya che mngon shes dang //
NK073(pu)001:1767: grangs dang yul gyi bla na med //
NK073(pu)001:1768: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i mngon shes kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1769: g.yo thob 'byung bar the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1770: lus ngag sems kyi mthu rtags kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1771: cho 'phrul bzhi tshul g.yo thob byed //
NK073(pu)001:1772: gzhan yang sngon bas gsal brtan pa //
NK073(pu)001:1774: spyod lam kun tu legs nyes kun //
NK073(pu)001:1775: gsal bar 'byung zhi shin tu brtan //
NK073(pu)001:1776: bsam gtan 'bad pa bzlas pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1777: sgrub pa po ni rtag tu mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1778: sangs rgyas mthu dang mtshungs par mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1779: sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK073(pu)001:1780: bdag med pa ni myur du mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1781: sems dpa' chen po khams gsum pas //
NK073(pu)001:1782: mchod pa byas par de mthong ngo //
NK073(pu)001:1784: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK073(pu)001:1785: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga rnams kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1786: rtag tu mchod pa byas pa mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1787: rdo rje sems dpa'i gzugs chen dang //
NK073(pu)001:1788: grangs chen rdo rje'i mchog dag tu //
NK073(pu)001:1789: rmi lam dag na rang gzugs mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1790: grags chen rdo rje gsang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1791: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor lo can //
NK073(pu)001:1792: sangs rgyas chen po phyag btsal ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:1794: lus ngag sems kyi mthu las skyes //
NK073(pu)001:1795: rgyan rnams thams cad yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1796: lha yi bu mo yid 'ong dang //
NK073(pu)001:1797: khye'u dang bu mo dag mthong na //
NK073(pu)001:1798: de ni dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1799: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1800: zhing na gnas par nges par mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1801: thugs ni dgyes par gyur nas kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1802: chos mdzod yid du 'ong la sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1803: chos kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i sku //
NK073(pu)001:1804: sems can kun gyis yongs bskor ba //
NK073(pu)001:1805: bsam gtan rdo rje la gnas pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1806: dam tshig sbyor bar mthong bar 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1807: sna tshogs kun dga' skyed mos tshal //
NK073(pu)001:1808: lha yi bu la sogs pas brgyan //
NK073(pu)001:1809: sangs rgyas kun gyi byin rlabs las //
NK073(pu)001:1810: bsam gtan dam tshig can gyis mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1811: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK073(pu)001:1812: de ni mngon par dbang bskur mthong //
NK073(pu)001:1813: rig 'dzin rgyal po chen po yis //
NK073(pu)001:1814: bskor ba byas pa de mthong ngo //
NK073(pu)001:1815: rdo rje las byung sna tshogs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:1816: rmi lam dri med de mthong na //
NK073(pu)001:1817: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las //
NK073(pu)001:1818: skye pa bla na med pa 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1819: gdol pa khyi yi sbyor la sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1820: rdo rje 'dzin pas mthong na ni //
NK073(pu)001:1821: blo ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK073(pu)001:1823: yi ge phyag rgya rnam gnyis kyi //
NK073(pu)001:1824: skye mched mthong ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:1825: lha yi sku ni gsal bsgom na //
NK073(pu)001:1826: bsod nams tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1827: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK073(pu)001:1828: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1829: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK073(pu)001:1831: ye nas mnyam nyid sbyor bas su //
NK073(pu)001:1832: lha nyid du ni rtag tu bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1833: bder gshegs kun dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK073(pu)001:1835: dkyil 'khor kun dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:1836: sku gsung ye shes lnga rdzogs 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:1837: yi dam lha yi mtshan nyid ni //
NK073(pu)001:1838: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK073(pu)001:1839: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1840: dam tshig bsrungs dang sngags bzlas dang //
NK073(pu)001:1841: phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod pa bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:1842: brtson 'grus che zhing brtan par gzung //
NK073(pu)001:1844: mi 'grub nyen yang che bar gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:1845: ci ltar ral gri'i so la nan tan du //
NK073(pu)001:1846: legs par ma gzung lag pa chod par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1847: de bzhin nan tan med pa'i gsang sngags pa //
NK073(pu)001:1848: phung ba'am yang na 'bras bu med par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:1849: de bas bar chad brtson med na //
NK073(pu)001:1850: dper na sa bon tshig pa las //
NK073(pu)001:1854: gang zhig zhal mthong mos pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:1855: bsnyeen bkur mchod pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1856: mi dge mtshams med bco lnga sogs //
NK073(pu)001:1857: las ngan sbyangs te ril la sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:1858: gang gis mi rtag mthong na yang //
NK073(pu)001:1859: phyag rgya ma nyams gsal bzung ste //
NK073(pu)001:1861: a yang stobs kyis bskul bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:1862: rnam smin rigs la the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:1864: de nyid bar phyi'am lan grangs gzhan //
NK073(pu)001:1865: tshe yang phyi ma'am gzhan thob nges //
NK073(pu)001:1866: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1867: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs 'gyur zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1868: gsal ba'i yid gnyis med pa na //
NK073(pu)001:1870: 'di ltar bsgom zhing bsgrub byas na //
NK073(pu)001:1871: 'bras bu mngon du ma byung yang //
NK073(pu)001:1872: tshe rabs skye ba thams cad du //
NK073(pu)001:1873: lha mi mtshan rdzogs sdug bsngal sel //
NK073(pu)001:1874: bder gshegs 'byung dang mi bskol zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1876: byang chub gzungs la zhugs pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:1878: phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1880: // rang gi lha la phyag 'tshal te //
NK073(pu)001:1881: spros pa'i rnal 'byor bshad par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1882: spros pa'i bzhi po lha de dbur //
NK073(pu)001:1883: gzhag pas grol phyir rgyas par bshad //
NK073(pu)001:1884: rnal 'byor rnam gsum sngon rdzogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:1885: sa la sogs par phyag rgyar bcas //
NK073(pu)001:1886: ri mo rgyu bzhi'am 'bur blugs dang //
NK073(pu)001:1888: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan khang bu dngos //
NK073(pu)001:1889: ye shes byin ldan brten par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1890: ma h+aa ba ling a mri ta //
NK073(pu)001:1891: dmar chen phyi nang mchod pa bkram //
NK073(pu)001:1892: rol mo mchod sogs rgya chen rnams //
NK073(pu)001:1893: ci ltar 'os pa bzhin du bya //
NK073(pu)001:1894: phyogs bcing brgyad kyis rim rdzogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:1895: las kyi lha yi rnal 'byor gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1896: mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab par bya //
NK073(pu)001:1897: bdud rtsi'i chus bsang bgegs bskrad bdug /
NK073(pu)001:1898: bsod nams yongs su rdzogs bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:1899: spyod yul byin gyis brlabs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:1900: 'khor lo sa mthar dbyung ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:1901: tshogs la dus kyis bsgrub phyir bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1902: dgug btang bcing grol gso gsad dang //
NK073(pu)001:1904: gang dag gdul bya ji snyed pa //
NK073(pu)001:1905: spros pa'i las kyis gdon phyir ro //
NK073(pu)001:1906: gcig ni spros pa'ang rnam gnyis te //
NK073(pu)001:1907: rjes su mthun par zhi dang khro //
NK073(pu)001:1908: de re re'ang tshul gnyis kyis //
NK073(pu)001:1909: blo dang ldan par 'tshams ston yin //
NK073(pu)001:1910: snga ma'ang rim dang cig char ba //
NK073(pu)001:1911: phye bas phyi ma'ang bzhin 'jug pa //
NK073(pu)001:1912: nyi zla gza' skar dus gcig tu //
NK073(pu)001:1913: chu dkyil dwangs par gsal ba bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:1915: snying po brjod pas 'khor lo shar //
NK073(pu)001:1916: der sngon bstan pa bzhin 'jug pa //
NK073(pu)001:1917: mthong dang snga ma'i rnal 'byor stobs //
NK073(pu)001:1918: thob pas shes bya slob tshul du //
NK073(pu)001:1919: du ma gcig gsal byed pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:1920: ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK073(pu)001:1921: 'khor lo tshom bu grangs zhal phyag /
NK073(pu)001:1922: dang po bco brgyad bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:1923: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor rim par slob //
NK073(pu)001:1924: gnyis pa bdag chag yab yum gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:1925: gnas pa'i 'khor lo gsal byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1926: gdan ldan dbus na bdag po gnas //
NK073(pu)001:1927: de la sems dpa' khro bos bskor //
NK073(pu)001:1928: brtan nas mdun rgyab sku gsung thugs //
NK073(pu)001:1930: mi yi dbang du tshom bu gsum //
NK073(pu)001:1931: shin tu goms par bya ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:1932: brtan nas g.yas dang g.yon nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:1933: yon tan phrin las dkyil 'khor gzhag /
NK073(pu)001:1934: rnal 'byor dbang du tshom bu lnga //
NK073(pu)001:1935: shin tu 'dris nas dus tshogs sbyar //
NK073(pu)001:1936: gsum pa rtsa ba'i sku nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:1937: brtan pas sku gsung gtso bor gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1938: gsum 'chor med na yon tan las //
NK073(pu)001:1939: lnga rdzogs yab yum zung brtan nas //
NK073(pu)001:1940: lnga pa'i don spros bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:1941: ma bcos ngang gis gnas pa las //
NK073(pu)001:1942: ye shes lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1943: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1944: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK073(pu)001:1946: stangs dpyal gnyis kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:1947: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK073(pu)001:1948: ri rab til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:1949: dpe byad mtshan gyis rgyas spras pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:1950: de ltar gtso mchog ldan byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1951: bya byed rigs bzhi'am stong bsgom bya //
NK073(pu)001:1953: nyi khri bzhi stong dus gcig gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1954: phyogs bcu ma lus gzhal yas khang //
NK073(pu)001:1955: nyi zla gza' skar gdan dang rgyan //
NK073(pu)001:1956: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor ma lus bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1957: bsam yas lhun grub nyid la slob //
NK073(pu)001:1958: bzhi pa zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK073(pu)001:1959: brtan nas gsum la'ang de bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1960: lnga pa'ang rjes su mthun bsgom nas //
NK073(pu)001:1961: spros pa'i zhal phyag rdzogs gsal ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:1962: bsgyur ba'i 'khor lo'ang de bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1963: dang po lnga bcu brgyad goms nas //
NK073(pu)001:1964: drug cu rtsa brgyad de bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:1965: dbus kyi he ru bzhi po la //
NK073(pu)001:1966: sku gsum mdun rgyab khrag 'thung gsal //
NK073(pu)001:1967: de brtan 'khor dang bcas pa bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:1968: sku gsung thugs la brtan byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:1969: g.yas g.yon yon tan las khro bo //
NK073(pu)001:1970: yab yum gsal nas 'khor lo lha //
NK073(pu)001:1971: rdzogs par bsgom pa'i rim bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:1972: gang byas ma sun gyen du 'phar //
NK073(pu)001:1973: rjes su mthun pas 'jigs byed kyang //
NK073(pu)001:1974: gcig dang gnyis dang gsum bzhi lnga //
NK073(pu)001:1975: yab yum mthar phyin 'khor lo'i chas //
NK073(pu)001:1976: lnga bcu'i tshom bu gnas yul dang //
NK073(pu)001:1977: sgo slas h'u chen brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK073(pu)001:1978: yan lag bkod pa lnga bcu brgyad //
NK073(pu)001:1979: cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:1980: dgu bcu'i lha rnams yan lag ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1981: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gsum phyag drug /
NK073(pu)001:1982: dgu dang bco brgyad kun dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1983: nyi shu rtsa gcig bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:1984: dgu brgyad stong brgyad brgya zhal phyag /
NK073(pu)001:1985: grangs med bar du slob byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:1986: rim thabs brjod kyi spyod yul na //
NK073(pu)001:1987: nyi shu gcig dang dgu brgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:1988: grangs med mthar phyin rim par ldan //
NK073(pu)001:1989: de ltar ldan pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK073(pu)001:1990: zhugs slob mthar phyin par skabs su //
NK073(pu)001:1991: rang bzhin yul nas dbab bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:1992: gzhug bcing brtan sogs ldan byas te //
NK073(pu)001:1993: rdzas dang ting 'dzin rim bzhin mchod //
NK073(pu)001:1994: bstod smon ldan nas bsnyen pa bya //
NK073(pu)001:1995: bar skabs lhag ma'i gnas bskangs nas //
NK073(pu)001:1996: dam bsgrag bcol zhing las la dgye //
NK073(pu)001:1997: 'khor lo bsdu bsrung spyod lam kun //
NK073(pu)001:1998: khro zhi'i man ngag gzhung bzhin bya //
NK073(pu)001:1999: phung sogs dkyil 'khor lhar snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:2000: rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan ji bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:2001: kun dngos rang rig lhar gsal ba //
NK073(pu)001:2002: gcig dang du ma yongs kyis med //
NK073(pu)001:2003: gsal la yul med mi g.yo ba //
NK073(pu)001:2004: rnal 'byor ngo bor rgyal bas gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:2005: rang bzhin spros pas rnal 'byor spros //
NK073(pu)001:2007: 'khor lo spros dang phyag rgya spros //
NK073(pu)001:2008: tshom bu spros dang zhal phyag spros //
NK073(pu)001:2009: kun nas spros phyir 'bras bu spros //
NK073(pu)001:2010: spros pas nyams gsal rnal 'byor sgra'o //
NK073(pu)001:2011: 'di tshe le lo rnam gnyis dang //
NK073(pu)001:2012: mtshan mtha' lnga dngos mthong 'dzin dang //
NK073(pu)001:2013: rnal 'byor bdud kyi yul mthong ba'ang //
NK073(pu)001:2014: sprul pa grangs med 'gyed pa mthong //
NK073(pu)001:2015: dam par 'dun mthong dam par smra //
NK073(pu)001:2016: rgyal bas gsung kun gsal mthong dang //
NK073(pu)001:2017: dus gsum gsal shes mthong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2018: rgyu drug lam gnas kun mthong dang //
NK073(pu)001:2019: de la snying rjes shugs 'byung dang //
NK073(pu)001:2020: kun kyang gsal bar mthong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2021: ci la'ang thogs med 'gro ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2023: rgyal bas phyag brkyang lung ston dang //
NK073(pu)001:2024: kun gyi skad du chos smra dang //
NK073(pu)001:2025: snod bcud bsti gnas mthong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2026: stong gsum mnyam par bkod pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2027: de nyid rang bzhin gsal snang dang //
NK073(pu)001:2028: las su rung bas thogs med dang //
NK073(pu)001:2029: dam pa'i don la bsgo ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2031: rang bzhin rtogs na dam pa'i rtags //
NK073(pu)001:2032: mi shes dga' brod byed pa bdud //
NK073(pu)001:2033: khe dang grags par dregs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2034: basngagasa pa thob pas mtshan mas g.yengs //
NK073(pu)001:2035: re dang dogs pa cung zad yod //
NK073(pu)001:2036: nga'am nga zhes che bas rgyal //
NK073(pu)001:2038: rgyu ba'i gzung 'dzin bye brag shes //
NK073(pu)001:2040: zung du 'brel bas skyed mthar phyin //
NK073(pu)001:2041: 'bras bu lam shes brtan pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:2042: bya ba med pa'i brtson 'grus blang //
NK073(pu)001:2043: mtshan ma rang rig cho 'phrul ba //
NK073(pu)001:2044: sems phyir mthong na re dogs med //
NK073(pu)001:2045: dper na nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK073(pu)001:2046: nyi zla gza' skar glog 'gyu dang //
NK073(pu)001:2048: nam mkha'i dbyings las 'gyur nyams med //
NK073(pu)001:2049: chos kyi dbyings ni mtha' yas par //
NK073(pu)001:2050: sku gsung rmad byung ngo mtshar dang //
NK073(pu)001:2052: de bzhin nyid la nyam 'gyur med //
NK073(pu)001:2054: bdag gnyis med shes nga rgyal med //
NK073(pu)001:2055: spyod yul mtshan ma gang mthong yang //
NK073(pu)001:2056: ye shes rang snang nyid du sbyar //
NK073(pu)001:2057: snang byed spros pa 'phel ba'i rim //
NK073(pu)001:2058: bslab pa'i rim pa ji bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:2059: sngon bstan mod kyang 'dir slob pa //
NK073(pu)001:2060: ma goms dbang gis rnam par lnga'o //
NK073(pu)001:2061: gsum lnga lha gsal cung zad yod //
NK073(pu)001:2063: de gsal thun bzhi'i cha gsum du //
NK073(pu)001:2064: gsal ba mi g.yo gnyis pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:2065: thun brkyang nus pa gsum pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2066: de nyid rkyen dbang mi 'gro ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:2067: bzhi pa khyad par gang gnas pa //
NK073(pu)001:2068: shin tu mi 'phrogs lnga pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:2069: grangs la sbyar na mthar thal 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2070: de bas nyams tshod zin pa gces //
NK073(pu)001:2071: rnal 'byor chen po'i lta spyod ni //
NK073(pu)001:2072: ci ltar spyad kyang rang bzhin med //
NK073(pu)001:2073: mkha' la bya chen lding ba bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2074: chu la nya chen 'phyo ba bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2075: rnal 'byor lta ba de ltar blta //
NK073(pu)001:2076: rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:2077: thams cad kun la dbyer med spyod //
NK073(pu)001:2078: bde ba'i ro mchog myong gyur te //
NK073(pu)001:2079: de la su zhig chags par byed //
NK073(pu)001:2080: bde ba'i mchog nyid bsod nams tshogs //
NK073(pu)001:2081: de lta bu yi ngang du spyod //
NK073(pu)001:2082: 'di ni spyod pa rlabs chen yin //
NK073(pu)001:2083: lta spyod ya char ma gyur pas //
NK073(pu)001:2084: sngags 'chang rnams kyis rtag tu spyad //
NK073(pu)001:2085: lnga bzhi spang bya dman spyod kun //
NK073(pu)001:2086: bdag dang gzhan phyir 'jol nyog ste //
NK073(pu)001:2087: gang yang byas la ma thogs shing //
NK073(pu)001:2089: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK073(pu)001:2090: rnam smin du shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2091: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2092: yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2093: gzugs sgra dri ro re la sogs //
NK073(pu)001:2094: rnam smin m+au du shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2095: yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2096: yang na khro mo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2097: spyod yul lha dang lha mor rol //
NK073(pu)001:2098: 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang //
NK073(pu)001:2099: sna tshogs snang ba thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2100: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK073(pu)001:2101: gzugs mdzes lha dang lha mor brtag /
NK073(pu)001:2102: thams cad kun tu bzang po yis //
NK073(pu)001:2103: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:2104: thogs pa med par spyad bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:2105: bsod nams tshogs chen yin par brtags //
NK073(pu)001:2106: de bzhin gshegs pa lngar yang brtags //
NK073(pu)001:2107: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK073(pu)001:2108: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod yon rnams //
NK073(pu)001:2109: rab 'bring tha ma thams cad spyad //
NK073(pu)001:2110: dang du blang dang mi spang ba //
NK073(pu)001:2111: rnal 'byor pa yis rtag tu spyad //
NK073(pu)001:2112: chags pa med par gyur pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2113: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por ni //
NK073(pu)001:2114: dam tshig mdo bshad nang nas byung //
NK073(pu)001:2115: spyod yul mthong thos thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2118: ma nyams de yi dbyings na gnas //
NK073(pu)001:2119: shes rab mchog gis rtag tu spyod //
NK073(pu)001:2120: yang na dam tshig 'di lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:2121: ji ltar spyod kyang sdom mi 'da' //
NK073(pu)001:2122: thams cad ma lus sangs rgyas la //
NK073(pu)001:2123: bsgrub cing bsrung bar bya ba'ang med //
NK073(pu)001:2124: dge dang mi dge gnyis ka med //
NK073(pu)001:2125: de la bsrung du rdul tsam med //
NK073(pu)001:2126: gzhan phyir grags pa'i bsrung bya kun //
NK073(pu)001:2128: rdo rje sems dpa'i bkas bshad pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2129: sdom pa'i rtsa ba thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2130: de bzhin du ni ma bsrung na //
NK073(pu)001:2131: yak+sha khro bo'i me dbal gyis //
NK073(pu)001:2132: snying nas drangs te khrag 'thung nas //
NK073(pu)001:2133: ngan song gsum du skye bar 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2134: de yi sdug bsngal bzod glags chad //
NK073(pu)001:2135: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod //
NK073(pu)001:2136: shing bal lta bu shin tu yang //
NK073(pu)001:2137: dbugs kyi rgyu ba yun ring bral //
NK073(pu)001:2138: rnal 'byor mkha' la gza' skar bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2139: gsal la mi g.yo spyod yul med //
NK073(pu)001:2140: zhor las byung ba kun rdzogs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2142: las su rung ba'i rtag rnam kyang //
NK073(pu)001:2143: sngon byung stobs su 'phel ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2144: khams snyoms rang lus bde bas rgyas //
NK073(pu)001:2145: 'du ba bzhi bral bzod thob tshe //
NK073(pu)001:2146: mngon shes drug dang rtsa lnga rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:2147: rab 'bring cha yis yul khams gling //
NK073(pu)001:2148: tshun chad gsal zhing 'dul bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:2149: tshogs drug dag pa'i stobs las gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2150: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu cha g.yo thob //
NK073(pu)001:2151: thams cad skad mthun chos ston rjes //
NK073(pu)001:2152: sa g.yos chos snang byed pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2153: yi ge sgra byed kun brjod pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2154: 'di dag mthong dang bco brgyad dang //
NK073(pu)001:2155: shugs snang brgyad mthong re dogs gzhan //
NK073(pu)001:2156: rmi lam nyid dang chos mthun par //
NK073(pu)001:2157: 'byung ba gsal dang brtan pas phyes //
NK073(pu)001:2158: bzang ba'i lta bu lung bstan kun //
NK073(pu)001:2161: mthar phyin rigs kyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2162: mtshan ma 'byung ba'i sa yin te //
NK073(pu)001:2163: bar chad med tshogs skabs su'ang 'adi'o //
NK073(pu)001:2164: phung po lnga nyid de bzhin gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:2165: dbang po rnam shes byang chub sems //
NK073(pu)001:2166: yul dus byang chub chen mo yin //
NK073(pu)001:2167: bdag rtog rnam bzhi khro bo bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:2168: rtag chad mu bzhi khro mo yin //
NK073(pu)001:2169: de sems rang rig nyid ces bya //
NK073(pu)001:2170: de bzhin mnyam rdzogs lhun grub pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2171: de bzhin gshegs dang ye shes lnga //
NK073(pu)001:2172: rang byung chen po'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2173: rtog gnyis bral ba'i thabs mkhas kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2174: lhar gsal dngos po med bsgom na //
NK073(pu)001:2175: mthong thos la sogs med pa'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:2176: rang rig ye shes gsal bsgom nas //
NK073(pu)001:2177: rang bzhin med par cir yang 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2178: rkyen gyis bsgyur ba'i dus 'byung na //
NK073(pu)001:2179: spros pa gang yin gzung ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:2180: las ngan lam zhen rgyun bcad nas //
NK073(pu)001:2181: bar ma'am phyi mar gnyis sbyor 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2182: gang zhig nus gzhan skal med pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:2184: tshe rabs kun tu bde thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:2185: gsum dang mi bsgom spyad pas 'thob //
NK073(pu)001:2186: snyoms las med par brtson byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:2187: lam du rigs 'dzin thob pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:2188: chos nyid dam tshig smon mthu dang //
NK073(pu)001:2190: spros pa'i rnal 'byor rgyun chags pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2191: bsod nams ye shes longs spyod kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2192: mun snang stug 'gyur rtsi bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:2193: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs mchog mnyes //
NK073(pu)001:2194: spros pa'i rnal 'byor la bslab pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2197: bar chad med par sbyor ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:2198: sgrub pa dus kyi tshogs bshad bya //
NK073(pu)001:2199: bar chad med pa'i lam sgrub pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2200: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK073(pu)001:2201: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK073(pu)001:2202: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2204: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing //
NK073(pu)001:2205: sa dang bar snang shis pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2206: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2207: yid 'ong sa btsal rgyas par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2208: rnyed nas tshom bu'i grangs bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:2209: che chung rkyen du 'tshams par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2210: 'khor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2211: rin chen byug pas bsrungs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2212: rin chen spros pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK073(pu)001:2213: yid 'ong bya ba shin tu gces //
NK073(pu)001:2214: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK073(pu)001:2215: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK073(pu)001:2216: byang chub spyod pa cher spyod pa //
NK073(pu)001:2217: gsang mchog dngos grub myur ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2218: gza' skar shis pa blang bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:2219: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK073(pu)001:2220: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK073(pu)001:2221: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi mchog bsgrub phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2223: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2224: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams dang //
NK073(pu)001:2225: dkyil 'khor yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK073(pu)001:2226: dngos grub rten dang bar chad bzlog /
NK073(pu)001:2227: yo byad dag par bsdu bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:2228: tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis brlab //
NK073(pu)001:2229: sgrub thabs yan lag bzhi sbyar ba //
NK073(pu)001:2230: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK073(pu)001:2231: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:2232: dang po dam mnos bzhin du bya //
NK073(pu)001:2233: dam bcas ldan pas 'dus te bsgrub //
NK073(pu)001:2234: yang na dpag tshad rgyang grags sam //
NK073(pu)001:2235: so sor 'tshams pa'i gzugs brnyan bri //
NK073(pu)001:2236: rgyan dang mchod sogs 'khor ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2237: phyi rol mchod pa'i las rdzogs te //
NK073(pu)001:2238: phyi bcad bsrung sgo rim pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2239: bsnyen pa'i don du sngon bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:2240: rdzogs pa'i las rnams zin par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2241: 'dus pas phyogs bcing rdzas brlabs nas //
NK073(pu)001:2242: spyi'am yang na re re zhing //
NK073(pu)001:2243: tshob bu 'khor lo rim bzhin bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2244: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2245: de bzhin gshegs dang yum du bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2246: sems dpa' sems ma nyid du bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2247: so so'i rigs dang phyag rgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:2248: ting 'dzin yang dag so sor gsal //
NK073(pu)001:2249: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK073(pu)001:2250: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK073(pu)001:2251: khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2252: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2253: de bzhin rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK073(pu)001:2254: pad+ma'i rigs te sku gsung thugs //
NK073(pu)001:2255: khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2256: tshom bu gsum pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2257: lnga dang lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:2258: tshom bu lnga yi lha bkod la //
NK073(pu)001:2259: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcu //
NK073(pu)001:2260: 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2261: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK073(pu)001:2262: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen pos //
NK073(pu)001:2263: rdzogs pa'i skabs 'dir shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2264: 'di yang lam sgrub sbyor ba yi //
NK073(pu)001:2265: cha yi dang po bsnyen pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:2266: byang chub sems rtogs 'grus pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:2267: bsnyen pa'i dam pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2268: sems chas snying rje man chad do //
NK073(pu)001:2269: phyag rgya gsal ba nye bsnyen pa //
NK073(pu)001:2270: de phyir gcig dang spros pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2271: sgrub pa nyid na bar chad med //
NK073(pu)001:2272: dus kyi tshogs mthar sgrub chen len //
NK073(pu)001:2274: gsum pa mchod pa'i skabs su shes //
NK073(pu)001:2275: gnyis pa gtso bor 'dir bstan pa //
NK073(pu)001:2276: gzhi dang gzhung gis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2277: phun sum tshogs pa lnga gzhi la //
NK073(pu)001:2278: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yis gzhung bsrang ba'ang //
NK073(pu)001:2279: gang dag mos pa ci bzhin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2280: zhi dang khro bos bsgrub par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2281: de la snga ma gnas dang dus //
NK073(pu)001:2282: yo byad ston 'khor sgrub pa po //
NK073(pu)001:2283: bsgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:2284: bzhi dang sbyar bas gzhung rdzogs bya //
NK073(pu)001:2285: de la spros pa mthar phyin pas //
NK073(pu)001:2286: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs bya zhing //
NK073(pu)001:2287: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2288: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK073(pu)001:2290: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa bsgrub //
NK073(pu)001:2291: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:2292: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK073(pu)001:2294: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu brten //
NK073(pu)001:2295: byin rlabs dbang dang ldan byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:2296: rang bzhin gnas nas dbab bya ste //
NK073(pu)001:2297: gzhug cing brtan byas rim par mchod //
NK073(pu)001:2298: rdzogs nas bstan te bsnyen pa bya //
NK073(pu)001:2299: zin nas bsdus te rnal 'byor tshogs //
NK073(pu)001:2300: tshul bzhin mchod pa'i phrin las bya //
NK073(pu)001:2301: nang nub mkha' 'gro'i lhag ma sbyin //
NK073(pu)001:2302: bar chad bzlog phyir bsnyen pa bya //
NK073(pu)001:2303: zla phyed phyed zhag nye bsnyen pa //
NK073(pu)001:2305: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK073(pu)001:2307: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK073(pu)001:2308: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK073(pu)001:2309: de bzhin rgyud kyi zhag grangs bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2310: bar chad med par bsgrub par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2311: spyod lam yo byad lnga spyod cing //
NK073(pu)001:2312: dngos su mchod pa rnam gnyis po //
NK073(pu)001:2313: gtso ru dgos pa gang yin pa //
NK073(pu)001:2314: phyi ma gdug pa 'dul bar shes //
NK073(pu)001:2315: snga ma rgyas par bshad bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:2316: gos rgyan bza' btung glu gar rnams //
NK073(pu)001:2317: h'u du shes par rab spyad na //
NK073(pu)001:2318: ngo mtshar dkyil 'khor mnyes pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2319: gsang sogs yo byad lnga po rnams //
NK073(pu)001:2320: rigs phyir ma skyes ye shes gsal //
NK073(pu)001:2321: chos nyid ye shes rol par bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2322: gcig shos che'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:2323: phyogs bcu mtha' yas dus bzhi yi //
NK073(pu)001:2324: thams cad dbyer med ma d+ha la //
NK073(pu)001:2325: nyi zla shar ba'i gzhal yas la //
NK073(pu)001:2326: pad+ma chags med gdan bting nas //
NK073(pu)001:2327: rin chen zad med pho brang sa //
NK073(pu)001:2328: che chung tshad dpag med pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2329: byang chub bde ldan dkyil 'khor la //
NK073(pu)001:2330: bde ldan byang chub rab bkod nas //
NK073(pu)001:2331: ma lus thams cad dbyings bsdus nas //
NK073(pu)001:2332: lus bskyod yan lag bsgul zhing bsigs //
NK073(pu)001:2333: dbang po lnga yi dkyil 'khor kun //
NK073(pu)001:2334: phyag rgya chen po yin par bshad //
NK073(pu)001:2336: bro sogs tshe na bsgom pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:2338: nyi zla 'khrugs pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK073(pu)001:2339: pad+ma chags med gdan bting nas //
NK073(pu)001:2340: thabs dang shes rab chags med tshul //
NK073(pu)001:2341: yan lag lnga po thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2342: rang bzhin yong gis dag pa la //
NK073(pu)001:2343: ting 'dzin de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'o //
NK073(pu)001:2344: ye nas ma bcos yong gis med //
NK073(pu)001:2346: dbu la de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor //
NK073(pu)001:2347: yan lag bzhi la rigs bzhi'i 'khor //
NK073(pu)001:2348: kha dog dbyibs dang phyag rgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:2349: thabs dang shes rab gsal bsgom ste //
NK073(pu)001:2350: phyogs bcur spro zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK073(pu)001:2351: gnas su bsdu zhing dkyil 'khor bstim //
NK073(pu)001:2353: bde gshegs zhing du rnam par sbyong //
NK073(pu)001:2354: yan lag chen po lnga bskyod na //
NK073(pu)001:2355: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor ma lus g.yo //
NK073(pu)001:2357: snyigs ma lnga yang rnam par dag /
NK073(pu)001:2358: bzang mdzes legs pa'i gos bgos nas //
NK073(pu)001:2360: de nas mthar thug med kyi bar //
NK073(pu)001:2361: ye shes lnga yis brgyan par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2362: rgyan mchog mdzes pas lus brgyan nas //
NK073(pu)001:2364: phyogs bcu gang bar dkyil 'khor spro //
NK073(pu)001:2365: bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK073(pu)001:2366: mi dmigs dbyings nas dkyil 'khor mchod //
NK073(pu)001:2367: 'dod lnga thabs dang shes rab gnas //
NK073(pu)001:2368: bde mchog ro'ang myong bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:2369: ma chags tshogs chen gnyis dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2370: bro gar thabs kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK073(pu)001:2371: glu dbyangs tshig gi sgra bsgrags na //
NK073(pu)001:2372: phyogs bcu skye gnas ma lus kun //
NK073(pu)001:2373: lhun grub rdo rje'i sku mthong zhing //
NK073(pu)001:2374: chos kyi dung chen sgra yang thos //
NK073(pu)001:2375: sgrib gnyis byang nas byang chub 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2376: bden mthong snyan bsgrags tshogs chen 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2377: chags med ye shes tshogs dang ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2378: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
