NK073(pu)001:2720: thugs rjes bzung zhing dbyings su bstim //
NK073(pu)001:2721: bro glu tshig dang lta stangs dang //
NK073(pu)001:2722: ting 'dzin yo byad thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2723: zhi ba'o tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK073(pu)001:2724: bro gar rtse 'jo la sogs bsgyur //
NK073(pu)001:2725: 'khor gyi phra men tshims byas te //
NK073(pu)001:2726: dbang du sdud dang bsgo ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2727: phyag rgyas bkye la bsdus te spyad //
NK073(pu)001:2728: de ltar bsgrub pas the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:2729: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2730: de lta bu yi longs spyod na //
NK073(pu)001:2731: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK073(pu)001:2732: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:2733: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2734: rtags cha sngon bzhin 'phel la brtan //
NK073(pu)001:2735: gling grangs mthong ba drug kyang 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:2736: sgra snyan rmi lam dag tu yang //
NK073(pu)001:2737: bde ba'i 'jig rten gnas rnams dang //
NK073(pu)001:2738: skye ba gang dag 'dzin pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2739: rig 'dzin lung ston brtag par bya //
NK073(pu)001:2740: zhag grangs bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2741: lus ma spangs par rig 'dzin sa //
NK073(pu)001:2742: yun ring chos kyi bde spyad pas //
NK073(pu)001:2743: bla med rdo rje sems dpa'i sa //
NK073(pu)001:2744: dpe byad mtshan gyis rgyan spras pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2745: mngon shes drug ldan thams cad mkhyen //
NK073(pu)001:2746: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol //
NK073(pu)001:2747: sangs rgyas zhing la dbang bsgyur te //
NK073(pu)001:2748: spyod yul kun tu ma d+ha la //
NK073(pu)001:2749: ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2750: de bas las dus rag lus sems //
NK073(pu)001:2751: dor byas brtson 'grus chen pos sbyar //
NK073(pu)001:2752: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK073(pu)001:2753: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2754: 'di lta bu yi las byas na //
NK073(pu)001:2755: 'bras bu mngon du ma gyur yang //
NK073(pu)001:2756: lus ngag yid la dbang thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:2758: las dang 'brel mi byin rlabs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2759: theg pa dman par yongs mi skye //
NK073(pu)001:2760: bsod nams ye shes dpung tshogs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2761: las kyi mun pa sbyang pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2762: ngan song gnas su yongs mi ltung //
NK073(pu)001:2763: gnas ngan longs spyod mi bde ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:2765: gzugs mchog dam pa ldan pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2766: rdo rje theg mchog brjed mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2767: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK073(pu)001:2768: lha mi gnas mchog sa skabs der //
NK073(pu)001:2769: lus byad bzang zhing yan lag rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:2770: dbang po tshang zhing lhag chad med //
NK073(pu)001:2771: skad gdangs snyan zhing 'gro don byed //
NK073(pu)001:2772: bdag gi longs spyod thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:2773: gzhan la gnas pa med par 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2774: tshan po che yi mthu stobs dang //
NK073(pu)001:2775: 'gro ba'i don du yang dag ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2776: gzhan la gnod pa yongs mi byed //
NK073(pu)001:2777: snying rje che zhing shes rab ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2778: mthu stobs ldan zhing thabs ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:2779: bdag dang gzhan don rdzogs par byed //
NK073(pu)001:2780: mthar phyin skye shi med pa'i sa //
NK073(pu)001:2781: sangs rgyas yon tan rin po che //
NK073(pu)001:2782: bkod pa'i gzhal yas thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:2783: 'dod lha drug pa ci lta bar //
NK073(pu)001:2784: dbang bsgyur spyod pa'i dngos grub thob //
NK073(pu)001:2785: de phyir dbang bsgyur phyi ma'i dus //
NK073(pu)001:2786: nyid du sbyor ba'ang smos ci dgos //
NK073(pu)001:2787: de ltar brtson 'grus ldan pas ni //
NK073(pu)001:2788: mthong dang phyi mar gyur na yang //
NK073(pu)001:2789: lan grangs gzhan du'ang bdun nyid las //
NK073(pu)001:2791: cho ga sngags dang yo byad dag /
NK073(pu)001:2792: bco lnga rdzogs nas ma nyams ldan //
NK073(pu)001:2793: nges par 'tshogs te tshogs spyad na //
NK073(pu)001:2794: 'bras bu mngon du ma byung yang //
NK073(pu)001:2795: rgyal po bran mo ngan bshos kyang //
NK073(pu)001:2797: mthong nas dmangs kyi blar 'gyur zhing //
NK073(pu)001:2798: kun la dbang bsgyur stobs ldan la //
NK073(pu)001:2799: lha rnams re ba'i mthu skye bas //
NK073(pu)001:2800: bsrung sbed mchod pa byed pa ltar //
NK073(pu)001:2801: rnal 'byor stobs dang ldan gyur na //
NK073(pu)001:2802: rdo rje dam can ma lus kun //
NK073(pu)001:2803: de yi dbang gis khur bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:2804: spyod yul dor nas phyag rgyar rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:2805: la la de ltar de nges na //
NK073(pu)001:2806: de ltar ma gyur bsod nams sa //
NK073(pu)001:2807: tshe rabs skye ba thams cad du //
NK073(pu)001:2808: las ngan lnga bcu brgyad spyod pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2809: sa gnas kun tu skye mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2812: rnam smin thob nas sngon bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:2813: 'di la the tshom ldan min pas //
NK073(pu)001:2814: skal ldan kun gyis rtag 'grus bya'o //
NK073(pu)001:2815: bar chad med pa'i lam tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2817: // dngos grub lhag pa'i mchog nyid la //
NK073(pu)001:2818: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yis mos byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:2819: bde chen sa la dgod pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2820: mthar phyin 'bras bu mtshan nyid bshad //
NK073(pu)001:2821: dus tshogs bar chad med pa nas //
NK073(pu)001:2822: lhag ma med dang yod pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2823: mya ngan 'das pa mthar sbyor ba //
NK073(pu)001:2824: thun mong lta bur zung du 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2825: de la thog mar bshad pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:2826: gcig dang du ma'i rnal 'byor la //
NK073(pu)001:2827: bstan byas nyid sa'am de thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:2828: zla drug bcu drug bsnyen bsgrub tshe //
NK073(pu)001:2829: rdo rje'i lus su ma gyur par //
NK073(pu)001:2830: stobs chung rkyen smon zhan pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2831: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lhag lus bzhag /
NK073(pu)001:2833: lha yi rnal 'byor gsal rdzogs smin //
NK073(pu)001:2834: lus kyi d+r+wa bas bsgribs 'gyur ba //
NK073(pu)001:2836: bral nas snang byed de rnams smin //
NK073(pu)001:2837: yid kyis lha yi gzugs bzung zhing //
NK073(pu)001:2838: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:2839: lha yi sku nyid gsal 'gyur na //
NK073(pu)001:2840: rnam par smin zhes de la gdags //
NK073(pu)001:2841: rgya mig rgya sa ci lta bar //
NK073(pu)001:2842: phyag rgya thob la ma rag pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2843: gzugs rdzogs stobs chen de kho na //
NK073(pu)001:2844: de la'ang dgongs spyod khyad par gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:2845: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho snga phyi dang //
NK073(pu)001:2846: rgyud mthun stobs chas ming grags pa //
NK073(pu)001:2847: lhag med 'byung med las lus med //
NK073(pu)001:2848: mya ngan 'das pa'i smin zhes brjod //
NK073(pu)001:2849: dkyil 'khor rol pa'i tshul spyod pas //
NK073(pu)001:2850: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa bdag gi don //
NK073(pu)001:2851: smin pa'i phrin las rdzogs byed pas //
NK073(pu)001:2853: de de'ang 'di dang phyi ma dang //
NK073(pu)001:2854: lan grangs gzhan du rab 'bring gis //
NK073(pu)001:2855: thob kyi bskal par mi 'gyang ste //
NK073(pu)001:2856: dgongs spyod brtson pa gtso phyir ro //
NK073(pu)001:2857: gal te bral ma thag pa ru //
NK073(pu)001:2858: rgya bzhi rdzogs par bdag gyur pa //
NK073(pu)001:2859: rdo rje lnga rdzogs rig pa 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2860: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'bras bus //
NK073(pu)001:2861: de phyir rgya che'i bar chad med //
NK073(pu)001:2862: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK073(pu)001:2863: bar chad med pa'ang smin pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2864: mngon par shes pa de ming can //
NK073(pu)001:2866: dpag tshad gling khams yul la sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:2867: phyi ma'i dus kyi tshogs bsgrub pas //
NK073(pu)001:2868: dgongs spyod brtson pa stobs rdzogs dang //
NK073(pu)001:2869: yo byad thabs kyis stobs las skyes //
NK073(pu)001:2870: gzhan pa'i yo byad rtags ldan pa //
NK073(pu)001:2871: dngos grub rol pa'i mthu las byung //
NK073(pu)001:2872: thabs rgyus phye bas so so yang //
NK073(pu)001:2873: lam las skyes pa'i mchog yin te //
NK073(pu)001:2874: de yang rgyu dus ngo bo grangs //
NK073(pu)001:2875: dgongs spyod mngon shes sbyor ba'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:2876: bzhi gnyis lus kyis rdzogs par bshad //
NK073(pu)001:2877: thabs dang drang ba rgyur bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:2878: shes rab rnam gsum goms byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:2879: ting 'dzin mnyam pa'i don rtogs te //
NK073(pu)001:2880: kun tu yangs pa chen po bsgom //
NK073(pu)001:2881: shes 'jug lnga rtogs goms pas ni //
NK073(pu)001:2882: zla zhag rgyud bzhin 'grub byed pas //
NK073(pu)001:2883: rdo rje'i lus su the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:2884: ming bzhi lus nyid de lta'o //
NK073(pu)001:2885: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK073(pu)001:2886: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK073(pu)001:2887: rab 'bring ci bzhin mi bslu bar //
NK073(pu)001:2888: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2889: rgyu 'bras dus cig rdzogs pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2890: rang rig nyid la dbang thob ste //
NK073(pu)001:2891: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:2892: brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK073(pu)001:2893: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2894: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:2895: tshogs spyod bsgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK073(pu)001:2896: lus khams skyes gnas zag pa zad //
NK073(pu)001:2897: rdo rje'i lus 'gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK073(pu)001:2898: mthong ba'i chos las mya ngan 'das //
NK073(pu)001:2899: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK073(pu)001:2901: lha mi rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2902: lha dang mi dang tshangs pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:2903: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:2904: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK073(pu)001:2905: cha byad de nyid kyis chos ston //
NK073(pu)001:2907: dbang bsgyur 'jigs pa lnga sogs bral //
NK073(pu)001:2908: drug bzhi yan lag kun rdzogs shing //
NK073(pu)001:2909: rang dbang bsgyur ba'i skye ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:2911: rgyu yi dang por skal mnyam pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:2912: bdag phyir don du gnyer ba ni //
NK073(pu)001:2913: brgya phrag bcu drug tshe yis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:2914: gzhan du rang dbang thob pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2915: bskal pa grangs med gnas 'gyur yang //
NK073(pu)001:2916: sku ni shin tu gzhon pa'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:2918: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2920: lam mchog rdzogs pa'i rim pa'ang bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:2921: bcu dbang dang po'i 'dra mod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:2922: de nyid mthu yis zag mi zag /
NK073(pu)001:2923: rgyu dang ngo bo rnam pa gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:2924: de bas dgongs spyod smos ci dgos //
NK073(pu)001:2925: gzhan las 'grub pas de rigs min //
NK073(pu)001:2926: mchog la'ang yon tan mtshan chas brjod //
NK073(pu)001:2927: lus dang phung por bcas pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:2928: gnas par dbang ba'i rigs 'grub phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2930: zag kun zad pa'i rigs chen 'di //
NK073(pu)001:2931: ji ltar spyad kyang ldog pa med //
NK073(pu)001:2932: rang dbang thob pas dbugs byung phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2933: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK073(pu)001:2934: mkhas rtogs goms spyod rig pa 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2935: lha la sogs pa rdo rje 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:2936: mi gtong gzungs las mi thob pa //
NK073(pu)001:2937: yon tan grangs kyis bsam mi khyab //
NK073(pu)001:2938: dngos su sa khams lung ston pa //
NK073(pu)001:2939: rdo rje rdo rje bos dbang bskur //
NK073(pu)001:2940: mthong goms mthur ldan rig pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:2941: snang ba rig pa 'dzin pa'i gnas //
NK073(pu)001:2942: rig snang gnas la nges pa med //
NK073(pu)001:2943: skye ba cha byad don gyis 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:2944: chos rnam bdag phyir dmigs med phyir //
NK073(pu)001:2945: chos kun mi mthong chos nyid kyang //
NK073(pu)001:2946: mi mthong sangs rgyas thugs mi mthong //
NK073(pu)001:2947: snod bcud mi mthong ga nga mthong ba //
NK073(pu)001:2948: des ni yang dag bden pa mthong //
NK073(pu)001:2949: de bas thos myong rig sogs lam //
NK073(pu)001:2950: shes 'jug bar chad med las skyes //
NK073(pu)001:2951: de phyir mngon sum rtogs mchog ni //
NK073(pu)001:2952: rang dbang thob nas sngon bzhin te //
NK073(pu)001:2953: zag gsum zag pa 'di la med //
NK073(pu)001:2954: sngon chad lam gyi 'du byed med //
NK073(pu)001:2955: de yi re dogs chags bral las //
NK073(pu)001:2956: rim pa'am rim pa med tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:2957: stong khri la sogs grangs mang lha //
NK073(pu)001:2960: de ming dbang bsgyur rnal 'byor te //
NK073(pu)001:2961: brgya phrag cha rdzogs dus bar du //
NK073(pu)001:2962: goms byas gnyis thob mtha' skad cig /
NK073(pu)001:2963: cha yis rdo rje dpa' bor sbyor //
NK073(pu)001:2964: rigs mthun mchog brgya sprul pa las //
NK073(pu)001:2965: gsang thos bsam rig bsgor sbyor bas //
NK073(pu)001:2966: dkyus sar phyin pa'i cang shes bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2967: kun tu 'gro ba bdag po'i don //
NK073(pu)001:2968: rdzu 'phrul chos snang rjes ston brjod //
NK073(pu)001:2969: drug shes de min ldan pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:2970: dbang bsgyur rtsa ba rdo rje skus //
NK073(pu)001:2971: bya byed rdzogs par grub pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:2972: bzhi yi thog mas don spyod pa //
NK073(pu)001:2973: nus mthu can du dbang bsgyur nas //
NK073(pu)001:2975: chu rgyun bzlog dang rlung mi 'gul //
NK073(pu)001:2976: ri brag la sogs thogs med 'dzul //
NK073(pu)001:2977: chu la mi bying mes mi tshig /
NK073(pu)001:2979: mi snang ba dang mang por sprul //
NK073(pu)001:2980: gzhan yang ci ltar 'dod pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:2981: lha srin rnams la dbang bsgyur dang //
NK073(pu)001:2982: tshe dang dus la bsring sdud dang //
NK073(pu)001:2983: stong gsum yungs 'brur shong ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2984: yungs 'brus stong gsum gang ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2985: ba spu gang bsdu'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:2986: bsreg pa'i bskal pa gzhil ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2988: skams sar chu 'byung bye ma gser //
NK073(pu)001:2989: sol ba ljon shing 'byung ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:2990: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung dang //
NK073(pu)001:2991: 'bar nas me yang tshig pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:2992: chu rgyun bab ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:2994: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK073(pu)001:2995: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK073(pu)001:2996: ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:2997: sbrul dang gcan gzan gdug pa rnams //
NK073(pu)001:2999: bdud dang gdug pa la sogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3001: lus ma bor bar rig 'dzin nas //
NK073(pu)001:3002: thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3003: so so'i skad dang mthun pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:3004: so sor thar pa'i lam yang ston //
NK073(pu)001:3005: ngan song stong zhing bskul ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:3006: lam stegs dgod cing de dag nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3007: theg chen lam la dgod par mdzad //
NK073(pu)001:3008: thar pa bskul zhing zhi ba slong //
NK073(pu)001:3009: sa bcu shes bya sbyong byed cing //
NK073(pu)001:3010: bde gshegs 'khor la'ang chos ston mdzad //
NK073(pu)001:3011: stong gsum brgya bcu'i 'jig rten rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3012: g.yo dang rab g.yo shin tu g.yo //
NK073(pu)001:3013: mdzad pa snang ba de gnas rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3014: nang g.yos pa yis rim g.yos byed //
NK073(pu)001:3015: gsang ba sngags kyi sgra bsgrags pas //
NK073(pu)001:3016: kun kyang rmad byung sngags kyi sgrar //
NK073(pu)001:3017: grags pas bdud 'dul ngan song sbyong //
NK073(pu)001:3018: 'gro ba ma lus don yang byed //
NK073(pu)001:3019: las rnams thams cad kun byas nas //
NK073(pu)001:3020: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung thob //
NK073(pu)001:3021: mtshan dang dpe byad kun gyis brgyan //
NK073(pu)001:3022: mthar phyin bya ba med par 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:3023: rgyud las gsungs pa lnga bzhi ni //
NK073(pu)001:3024: spyod pa bcu gnyis phrin las rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3025: dbang bsgyur nyid du thogs med par //
NK073(pu)001:3026: sngon bzhin yul khyon 'dul bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:3027: skye mched rang byung ye shes phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3028: de nyid gcig dang du ma'i mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:3029: gnyis su med par mngon rtogs goms //
NK073(pu)001:3030: mthong bas dri ma drig sbyang phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3031: de snyed gzugs sgra dri ro reg /
NK073(pu)001:3032: shes pa'i bye brag rtsa lngar ldan //
NK073(pu)001:3033: gcig gis yul lnga gcod par byed //
NK073(pu)001:3034: tshang dang ma tshang 'jigs dogs med //
NK073(pu)001:3035: gzhan du lha yi rna ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:3036: spyan gyi mngon bar shes pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3037: sngon gnas rjes su dran pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3038: pha rol rnams kyi sems shes dang //
NK073(pu)001:3040: rdzu 'phrul shes pa'am zag zad shes //
NK073(pu)001:3041: de snyed tshun chad yul shes pas //
NK073(pu)001:3042: gang dang gang rnams 'dul bar mdzad //
NK073(pu)001:3043: de ming ldog zag med pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3044: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi mtshan ma brjod //
NK073(pu)001:3045: bdag gam gzhan phyir dbang can des //
NK073(pu)001:3046: sku tshe tshad grangs ci snyed bar //
NK073(pu)001:3047: bzhugs mtha' rang gis bsgrub sbyor ba //
NK073(pu)001:3048: sngon bzhin rim dang cig char ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:3049: de yang snga ma mthong ba'i lam //
NK073(pu)001:3050: rang gi shes rab gsum goms pas //
NK073(pu)001:3051: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK073(pu)001:3052: gang goms mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK073(pu)001:3053: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin der //
NK073(pu)001:3054: yongs gyur lhun grub thob nas gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3055: phyi ma'i rigs mchog de nyid nas //
NK073(pu)001:3056: sngon bzhin goms pa gsum byas pas //
NK073(pu)001:3057: rgya dor cig char mthar 'gro ba //
NK073(pu)001:3058: chos nyid dam tshig smon mthu yin //
NK073(pu)001:3059: de nyid bar ma bshad bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:3060: sngon gyi lus kyis rdzogs par bya //
NK073(pu)001:3061: gcig dang du ma'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK073(pu)001:3062: 'byung lus sems phyir rang bzhin lha //
NK073(pu)001:3063: mthong goms bsags pa'i mthar bsgrub pas //
NK073(pu)001:3064: kun 'gro sgrib dag ngo bor ru //
NK073(pu)001:3065: rnam smin tshul gyis 'grub pa med //
NK073(pu)001:3068: gcig pas de nyid lam byas pas //
NK073(pu)001:3069: lhag ma bcas par bsnur bsgrub mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:3070: de nyid gyur pas nges pa med //
NK073(pu)001:3071: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK073(pu)001:3072: bsgom pas gang yin mngon 'gyur sku //
NK073(pu)001:3073: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK073(pu)001:3074: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK073(pu)001:3075: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK073(pu)001:3077: rang lus gdod nas phyag rgya cher //
NK073(pu)001:3078: bsgom pas mngon du 'gyur pa'i sku //
NK073(pu)001:3079: mtshan dpe bzhi mngon drug rdzogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3080: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs su grags //
NK073(pu)001:3081: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK073(pu)001:3082: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK073(pu)001:3083: de phyir sku tshe tshad med do //
NK073(pu)001:3084: bsnur zhing mngon du bya dang bral //
NK073(pu)001:3085: de nyid rigs gsum rigs bzhi dang //
NK073(pu)001:3086: lnga dang mchog lnga'i rigs 'dzin pas //
NK073(pu)001:3087: rnam pa bzhi ru sngon bzhin 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3088: mchog gi ming grangs gnyis dang gsum //
NK073(pu)001:3089: mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo zhing //
NK073(pu)001:3090: dbang bsgyur 'du byed dang bral bas //
NK073(pu)001:3091: zag pa med pa'i bsgom pa'i lam //
NK073(pu)001:3092: mi g.yo rnal 'byor nyid du'ang brjod //
NK073(pu)001:3093: rgyal bas lung ston dngos 'byung ba //
NK073(pu)001:3094: brtag pa'i bye brag 'di la'ang med //
NK073(pu)001:3095: ye shes sku yi rnal 'byor pa //
NK073(pu)001:3096: sangs rgyas gnyis pa'i spyan dgongs kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3097: rgyu mthun mod kyang mi g.yo thob //
NK073(pu)001:3098: shin tu brtan pa'i klung gnas pa //
NK073(pu)001:3099: grangs can 'khor lo kun tu snang //
NK073(pu)001:3101: mnyam bzhag ngang la ma g.yos bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3102: stong gi 'jig rten brgya stong phrag /
NK073(pu)001:3103: bcu yi rdul snyed 'jig rten dag /
NK073(pu)001:3104: zhing grangs med pa brgya stong phrag /
NK073(pu)001:3105: bcu yi rdul snyed zhing khams su //
NK073(pu)001:3106: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3107: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK073(pu)001:3108: bzhi dang drug sogs de bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:3109: drug dang lnga yi yan lag bcas //
NK073(pu)001:3110: shes pa'ang 'dra mod bzhi sogs kun //
NK073(pu)001:3111: de snyed yul gyi khyad par dang //
NK073(pu)001:3112: don rdzogs mthu dang gdul byas dpags //
NK073(pu)001:3113: rang gi mi g.yo mthong goms dang //
NK073(pu)001:3114: don du gnyer rim rtsol ba yis //
NK073(pu)001:3115: lam kun rdzogs pa'i byin stobs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3116: rnal 'byor bral nas lhun gyis grub //
NK073(pu)001:3117: lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag /
NK073(pu)001:3118: rtsol ba med par lhun grub thob //
NK073(pu)001:3119: de de mngon du byas pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:3120: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang //
NK073(pu)001:3121: rang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas de //
NK073(pu)001:3122: sngon bzhin bzhi brgyad dgod par bya //
NK073(pu)001:3123: snga ma'i rigs la mthu rdzogs pas //
NK073(pu)001:3124: bshad pa bzhin du dri ma dag /
NK073(pu)001:3125: sangs rgyas gnyis pa'i shes rab gsum //
NK073(pu)001:3126: lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs su 'byung //
NK073(pu)001:3127: gnas der sngon bzhin gsum rdzogs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3128: longs spyod gsang ba'i lung thos shing //
NK073(pu)001:3129: rang gi dgongs spyod nus pa can //
NK073(pu)001:3130: sa mthar dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK073(pu)001:3131: de ltar dag pa'i shes pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3132: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK073(pu)001:3133: lhun mnyam ngang la mi g.yo zhing //
NK073(pu)001:3134: mi rtog nyid du bzhugs pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:3135: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK073(pu)001:3136: skad cig rags las rigs 'dzin mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:3137: cha byad rgyal ba nyid du ste //
NK073(pu)001:3138: lnga po lhun gyis grub phyir na //
NK073(pu)001:3139: de 'dra de nyid rgyal tshab ston //
NK073(pu)001:3140: de mi gtong bas ming 'grub phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3141: nyid la skye shi mi mnga' phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3142: rdo rje'i sku yang gdul bya la //
NK073(pu)001:3143: sprul pa rnams ni 'da' tshul ston //
NK073(pu)001:3144: don 'grub la sogs ci lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:3145: bya ba lhun grub rnal 'byor ni //
NK073(pu)001:3147: mtha' ma'i ming grangs mthar phyin lam //
NK073(pu)001:3148: rang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK073(pu)001:3149: de nyid dang ni mthar sbyor lam //
NK073(pu)001:3150: yang dag rdzogs pa'i rgyal tshab pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3151: snga ma gsum dang dang po bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:3152: cha lugs rang gi rgyal tshab sdud //
NK073(pu)001:3153: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3154: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan mchog 'chang //
NK073(pu)001:3155: yi ge 'khor lo'ang sngon gzigs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3156: mi g.yo ba la mi rtog pa //
NK073(pu)001:3157: da dung mngon par mi rgya ste //
NK073(pu)001:3158: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3159: des na dgongs spyod rgya mtsho kun //
NK073(pu)001:3160: ye shes rtsal rdzogs bya byed pa'am //
NK073(pu)001:3161: mthar phyin bya bral la sogs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3162: ming grangs cha la brjod par zad //
NK073(pu)001:3163: nyid phyir rdo rje 'dzin rdzogs la //
NK073(pu)001:3164: skad cig dus kyi bslab rdzogs nas //
NK073(pu)001:3165: mtha' ma'i bag la nyal ba dag /
NK073(pu)001:3166: bcom ldan 'das par gyur pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:3167: de tshe de sgrib cha yod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3168: lhun grub rig 'dzin sar bzhugs nas //
NK073(pu)001:3169: zhing khams thug pa med pa dag /
NK073(pu)001:3170: 'dul phyir sprul sku mdzad pa'ang ston //
NK073(pu)001:3171: srid gsum 'gro ba mtha' yas su //
NK073(pu)001:3172: thugs rjes rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK073(pu)001:3173: don dang mthun pa 'ba' zhig ston //
NK073(pu)001:3174: mi mthun zhags pas 'khor ba gcod //
NK073(pu)001:3175: la lar lhums zhugs bltams pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3176: la lar khab dang rgyal srid dang //
NK073(pu)001:3177: la lar rab byung dka' thub mdzad //
NK073(pu)001:3178: chos spyod mya ngan 'das sogs ston //
NK073(pu)001:3180: g.yem la g.yem ston sdang la sdang //
NK073(pu)001:3181: dregs la ri dang mun la mun //
NK073(pu)001:3182: rlung la'ang de bzhin mthun mi mthun //
NK073(pu)001:3183: rgya mtsho lta bu thabs spyod dang //
NK073(pu)001:3184: phrin las de bzhin sa yis sgrol //
NK073(pu)001:3185: gsang ba'i tan+t+ra ston pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3186: de bzhin bsdu ba'ang mdzad pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3187: dman lus bsod nams ldan gnas su //
NK073(pu)001:3188: sna tshogs lus can rigs la bskor //
NK073(pu)001:3189: mngon shes drug ldan mtshan bzang dpag /
NK073(pu)001:3190: kun mkhyen ye shes mnga' ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3191: yul dang tshad med rgyal ba nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3192: ji ltar me long lta bu'i tshul //
NK073(pu)001:3193: mi mthun mtshan ma gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3194: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK073(pu)001:3195: bdag rtogs mtshan ma kun bcom nas //
NK073(pu)001:3196: rdo rje'i dbyings su thim par byed //
NK073(pu)001:3197: bdag med rang rig ye shes kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3198: dngos dang dngos min bag chags bsregs //
NK073(pu)001:3199: rang dang spyi yi chos rnams dang //
NK073(pu)001:3200: sems kyi phrag dog thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:3201: dngos po'i med par rtogs byas pa //
NK073(pu)001:3203: rdo rje rtse mo mchog thob pas //
NK073(pu)001:3204: yid tshod med dang bdud sde rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3205: tshar bcad dpa' bos de rjes la //
NK073(pu)001:3206: rgyan gyi 'khor lo ma d+ha la //
NK073(pu)001:3207: bsam yas lhun rdzogs kun mkhyen 'jog /
NK073(pu)001:3208: mnyam bzhag ye shes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK073(pu)001:3209: don du gnyer ba'i smon lam mthus //
NK073(pu)001:3210: nyi shu rtsa lnga gzhan las min //
NK073(pu)001:3211: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan dang //
NK073(pu)001:3212: phrin las rmad byung kun grags pa //
NK073(pu)001:3213: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:3214: rang byung ye shes gnas med yin //
NK073(pu)001:3215: de bas ngo mtshar cho 'phrul chos //
NK073(pu)001:3216: gzhan las yod thob ma yin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3217: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3218: de lta bu yi ngang du snang //
NK073(pu)001:3219: mun snang 'gyur rtsi ma gi ta //
NK073(pu)001:3220: ci bzhin ma spangs de nyid 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3221: 'khor ba ma spangs rnam par dag /
NK073(pu)001:3222: mya ngan mi 'da' ye nas gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3223: 'gro dang gnas par bya ba min //
NK073(pu)001:3224: rtog pa thams cad ye shes tshogs //
NK073(pu)001:3225: mnyam dang mi mnyam mnyam dang mnyam //
NK073(pu)001:3226: bya dang mi bya bya med byas //
NK073(pu)001:3227: grub dang ma grub thams cad grub //
NK073(pu)001:3228: de phyir rigs 'dzin tha snyad bral //
NK073(pu)001:3229: mthar phyin pa'i lam rnams bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3231: // rang bzhin nyid du mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3232: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid la mos //
NK073(pu)001:3233: srid pa rim dang rdzogs tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:3234: mngon byed don yod bshad par bya //
NK073(pu)001:3235: mtshan nyid tha ma'i tha ma ni //
NK073(pu)001:3236: ngo bo tshul dang khyad par gyis //
NK073(pu)001:3237: lus gsum mngon du snang ba rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3238: ji lta ba bzhin shes par bya //
NK073(pu)001:3239: lus gsum snga ma brjod bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:3240: sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:3241: yon tan phrin las rmad byung ba //
NK073(pu)001:3242: lnga la'ang lnga nyid ngo bor gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3243: e ma ho yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK073(pu)001:3244: rgyal ba'i rgyal ba lha yi lha //
NK073(pu)001:3246: de bzhin gshegs las de bzhin gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3247: bde gshegs las kyang bde gshegs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3248: rin chen nor bu bzhin du bzhugs //
NK073(pu)001:3249: chos drug nor bus mtshon pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:3250: gcig dang du ma kun bral ldan //
NK073(pu)001:3251: de de rigs dngos rigs bral ba //
NK073(pu)001:3252: nyi shu lnga ldan kun ngo bor //
NK073(pu)001:3253: mos bzhin de rigs mthun snang la //
NK073(pu)001:3254: yang dag nyid du 'di zhes med //
NK073(pu)001:3255: lnga nyid lnga lngar ldan snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:3256: rigs bdag yang dag sangs rgyas pas //
NK073(pu)001:3257: tha ma'i tha ma zhen bral ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:3259: gnyis su med pa de bzhin nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3261: de bzhin bde chen ngang nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:3262: zug rngu kun bral gnyis phyir gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3263: sangs rgyas sems can sems la son //
NK073(pu)001:3264: dbang phyug chen po'i skur bzhugs pa //
NK073(pu)001:3266: dngos po gnyis la bde longs spyod //
NK073(pu)001:3267: de nyid cha re brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:3269: dus gsum chos kun gcig pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:3270: rgyal ba nyid phyir sna tshogs chos //
NK073(pu)001:3271: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3272: de nyid d+harma k+aa yar gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3273: thams cad rang rig mngon sum snang //
NK073(pu)001:3274: zhen mtha' kun bral kun chub pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3275: rang byung ye shes chen po ni //
NK073(pu)001:3276: kun gzhi 'dul snang phyir sku mchog /
NK073(pu)001:3277: 'dod khams mtha' na rdzogs kyi bar //
NK073(pu)001:3278: sdug bsngal kun dang 'dod bsam snyoms //
NK073(pu)001:3279: 'gog zhing btang snyoms bde chen sogs //
NK073(pu)001:3280: yul med kun rol longs spyod che //
NK073(pu)001:3281: rta bdun ri bong can nyid kyi //
NK073(pu)001:3282: gzhal yas khang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3283: kun tu snang ba tha dad ltar //
NK073(pu)001:3285: ci ltar mkha' la 'jig med ltar //
NK073(pu)001:3286: mi rtog kun dngos rtag chen po //
NK073(pu)001:3287: rdo rje'i sku mchog skye 'jig med //
NK073(pu)001:3288: lnga pa nyid du rab tu grags //
NK073(pu)001:3290: rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang shes bya yi //
NK073(pu)001:3291: sgrib pa mtha' spang sems dpa' che'i //
NK073(pu)001:3292: rgyal po lnga sogs rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK073(pu)001:3293: mos spyod dang po'am dbang bsgyur rig /
NK073(pu)001:3294: rdo rje'i tshogs mthong phyir ming 'grub //
NK073(pu)001:3295: de la de yi dgongs bshad pa //
NK073(pu)001:3296: brjod dang brjod 'dra'i phyir nges pa //
NK073(pu)001:3297: yi ge med pa 'jal ba bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:3298: yi ge drug cu drug gsum rgyas //
NK073(pu)001:3299: mjal pa lnga nyid tshul go ba //
NK073(pu)001:3300: so so nyid dang gsang bdag gis //
NK073(pu)001:3301: snyan ma lnga ldan phyir thos pas //
NK073(pu)001:3302: gsang ba'i rgyud bshad thos zhes gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:3303: rang bzhin 'brel dang dbang dang bas //
NK073(pu)001:3304: dwangs pa'i chu dang nyi zla bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3305: ma skyes don gyi gsung mchog gis //
NK073(pu)001:3306: smra brjod med par rnam snang mdzad //
NK073(pu)001:3307: rig pa'i ye shes ming lnga pas //
NK073(pu)001:3308: de bzhin 'brel ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3309: rang bzhin gsang ba'i rgyud rnams kun //
NK073(pu)001:3310: nyi ma lta bur gsal bar snang //
NK073(pu)001:3311: me long lta bur chos brgyad kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3312: mtshan pa'i dbang phyug sku mthong bas //
NK073(pu)001:3313: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK073(pu)001:3314: rgyud la rdo rje don snang byed //
NK073(pu)001:3315: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK073(pu)001:3316: drug gi rtsa ba yan lag tshul //
NK073(pu)001:3317: tshangs pa'i ngag ltar las can la //
NK073(pu)001:3318: snang ba sha yi rna bas thos //
NK073(pu)001:3320: gsung rnams dngos la sgras rkyen pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3321: sgra ltar grags stong dbyer med par //
NK073(pu)001:3322: mthong thos byed pa'ang de nyid mathu'o //
NK073(pu)001:3323: dngos po gnyis chos yan lag bcas //
NK073(pu)001:3324: sems chen phyir na stong chen pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3325: ye shes zug rngu ldan bral ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:3326: bde ba chen po mchog gi thugs //
NK073(pu)001:3327: nam mkha' lta bur sems gsal stong //
NK073(pu)001:3328: chos kyi rang mtshan dbyer med kun //
NK073(pu)001:3329: yul med me long ltar gsal ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:3330: mngon sum kun gyi mchog yin te //
NK073(pu)001:3331: rnam par mi rtog mchog gi thugs //
NK073(pu)001:3332: chen po lta bur thams cad la //
NK073(pu)001:3333: mi 'byed blang dor med mnyam nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3334: mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo ba //
NK073(pu)001:3335: mnyam pa chen po'i mchog gi thugs //
NK073(pu)001:3336: thugs rje chen pos 'brel ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:3337: nyid kyi dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3338: bya byed med par rnam bzhi yis //
NK073(pu)001:3339: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs rje yin //
NK073(pu)001:3340: chos dang chos can kun bral bas //
NK073(pu)001:3341: rang spyi dbyer med dus gcig tu //
NK073(pu)001:3342: mkha' la 'ja' ltar gsal ba ni //
NK073(pu)001:3343: mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs mchog go //
NK073(pu)001:3344: phyogs dus ma lus mi lus pa //
NK073(pu)001:3345: rang rgyud med par rig snang bas //
NK073(pu)001:3346: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3347: phyogs bcu ma lus sangs rgyas zhing //
NK073(pu)001:3348: lhun rdzogs rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK073(pu)001:3349: gzhal yas khang dang gzung 'dzin dang //
NK073(pu)001:3350: bral ba'i rang bzhin rten pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3351: brten bcas med pa kun gyi gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3352: ma spangs lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3353: sna tshogs dkyil 'khor chen po rgyan //
NK073(pu)001:3354: rang bzhin ma sgrib gsal ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3355: sna tshogs 'od zer phyogs bcur gsal //
NK073(pu)001:3356: stobs sogs 'bras bu kun rdzogs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3357: gdan lnga'i bye brag rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:3358: 'dul ba'i bya ba tha dad pa //
NK073(pu)001:3359: zhi dang khro dang mi mos nyams //
NK073(pu)001:3360: bzhi phyir rnam bzhi rol pa rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3362: rnam bzhi'i bye brag tha dad pa //
NK073(pu)001:3363: re re'ang lnga lnga tshul gyis snang //
NK073(pu)001:3364: de rigs bzhi yi cha 'dzin pa //
NK073(pu)001:3365: las kyi rigs la lhun gyis grub //
NK073(pu)001:3366: rnam pa bzhi yis 'dul mdzad pa //
NK073(pu)001:3367: phyogs kyis 'dul ba'i rigs ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:3368: de ltar sbyang mtha' skyes bu sa //
NK073(pu)001:3369: rigs lnga cha re 'dzin byed kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3370: gcig shos sangs rgyas kun ngo bo //
NK073(pu)001:3371: nyid du snga phyi drang ba tsam //
NK073(pu)001:3372: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3373: tshul ni smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK073(pu)001:3374: de don phyogs tsam brjod bya ba //
NK073(pu)001:3375: drang don snga phyir sangs rgyas pa //
NK073(pu)001:3376: don dam gcig pur ma yin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3377: chu la chu ltar gcig pa med //
NK073(pu)001:3378: gcis shos bden par ma yin pas //
NK073(pu)001:3379: so so tha dad cha rigs mod //
NK073(pu)001:3380: bden pa gnyis med dbang 'gyur pa //
NK073(pu)001:3381: bdag dang gzhan gyi gnyis med de //
NK073(pu)001:3382: so sor med phyir der don pa //
NK073(pu)001:3383: mtha' rnams kun bral kun ldan pa //
NK073(pu)001:3384: rang snang zhen bral mngon byas pa //
NK073(pu)001:3386: ngo bo gcig la rgyud 'dres min //
NK073(pu)001:3387: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK073(pu)001:3388: drang ba tsam ste de nyid min //
NK073(pu)001:3389: chu la chu ltar 'dod pa'ang de'o //
NK073(pu)001:3390: bden pa'i tshul gyis skyon brjod pas //
NK073(pu)001:3391: dag pa'i ye shes gnas yin par //
NK073(pu)001:3392: tan+t+ra nyid las grags pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3393: bde gshegs mi gnas mnyam pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:3394: ngang du byon gsung brjod pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:3395: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3397: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3398: thun mong min pa'i rgyal ming grangs //
NK073(pu)001:3399: bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3400: bcom ldan 'das dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK073(pu)001:3401: dgyes chen brjod sogs mtha' yas kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3402: lus gsum grangs min khyad par can //
NK073(pu)001:3403: mdo ru brjod par chub par gyis //
NK073(pu)001:3404: lnga dang lnga lngar lhun grub pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3405: rgyal ba gsum rdzogs so so yi //
NK073(pu)001:3406: grub mtha' sa yi sangs rgyas la //
NK073(pu)001:3407: grangs rdzogs ngo bo byin rlabs las //
NK073(pu)001:3408: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK073(pu)001:3409: dpags pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK073(pu)001:3410: de tshul sa bzhi rgyal ba dag /
NK073(pu)001:3411: rgyud gcig 'dres dang grol smra ba //
NK073(pu)001:3412: 'di drang tsam yin bshad yin phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3413: rgyud kyi khyad par bsam las 'das //
NK073(pu)001:3414: ming grangs theg chen dman pa bas //
NK073(pu)001:3415: thun mong tshogs kyis bder gshegs shing //
NK073(pu)001:3416: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:3417: dus kyi dbang phyir snga ma bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3418: gshegs pa nyid dang gsang ba pa'ang //
NK073(pu)001:3419: bya ba'i lugs kyis shes rab dang //
NK073(pu)001:3420: cho ga'i rnal 'byor grangs rdzogs pas //
NK073(pu)001:3421: 'bras bu lam byas bder gshegs pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3422: rdo rje 'dzin par de bzhin gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3423: yang na bya rgod 'dab logs kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3424: dgon phug bye ma mda' sna ru //
NK073(pu)001:3425: sa ri dbang bskur ci bzhin nam //
NK073(pu)001:3426: w+aa ra n+aa s+ai'i bsil khang du //
NK073(pu)001:3427: dam pa'i rigs can dbang bskur nas //
NK073(pu)001:3428: rdo rje 'dzin thob ci bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:3429: thub pa'i dbang bo de ci bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3430: gshegs ba'i rgyu dang bya ba dang //
NK073(pu)001:3431: gnyis ka'i rgyud las grags bzhin no //
NK073(pu)001:3432: rnal 'byor gzhung gis don bsgrub nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3434: phyogs bcu sprul pa'i longs spyod skus //
NK073(pu)001:3435: byang chub lnga stobs dbang bskur bas //
NK073(pu)001:3436: 'og min nyid du don grub ste //
NK073(pu)001:3437: sprul pa dka' thub khog pa nas //
NK073(pu)001:3438: ye shes snang mdzad lus su gshegs //
NK073(pu)001:3439: ri rab rtse mor 'khor lo bskor //
NK073(pu)001:3440: de yang rtog pa'i gzugs sku yin //
NK073(pu)001:3441: thabs dang shes rab lam nyid kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3443: ci bzhin lhun grub ngang son par //
NK073(pu)001:3444: tshul dang ngo bos khyad par che //
NK073(pu)001:3445: don grub dka' thub lus can la //
NK073(pu)001:3446: phyogs bcu rgyal ba sprin bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:3447: 'dus pa gsang ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3448: srod dang tho rangs dus nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:3449: nyi zla bza' ba'i dbang byin cing //
NK073(pu)001:3450: rol pa'i ka ra bstab pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:3451: ye shes mtshan rdzogs dbang thob nas //
NK073(pu)001:3452: de bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3453: de phyir thun mong rnam gsum las //
NK073(pu)001:3454: bya ba bzhi dang chub pa bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:3455: bden par de bzhin gshegs pa brgyad //
NK073(pu)001:3456: grangs dang ngo bo tsam gyis 'phags //
NK073(pu)001:3457: de nas rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das //
NK073(pu)001:3458: thun mong mchog lugs snga ma bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3459: so so thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3460: rdo rje lta bu bzhi bskyed pas //
NK073(pu)001:3461: bdud bzhi nges bcom mya ngan bzhi //
NK073(pu)001:3463: mi mthun gzhung gis sangs rgyas pa //
NK073(pu)001:3464: lta spyod ting 'dzin lam rim bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3465: grub pa'i mtha' las khyad par ba //
NK073(pu)001:3466: lta ba'i sgrib pas phye ba yin //
NK073(pu)001:3467: des na dgyes pa'i longs spyod kyang //
NK073(pu)001:3468: mdo dang bya ba rnal 'byor gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:3469: rgyud las ci ltar gsungs pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3470: gang gis dgyes chen yin tshod min //
NK073(pu)001:3471: de phyir dgyes pa'i rim yod pas //
NK073(pu)001:3472: sa yi sangs rgyas rim yod phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3473: ming grong yon tan cha yin te //
NK073(pu)001:3474: ngo bo nyid kyis rnam par 'phags //
NK073(pu)001:3475: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3476: brod pa bskyed phyir kun tu 'od //
NK073(pu)001:3477: rdor 'dzin stug po bkod par bstan //
NK073(pu)001:3478: mthar thugs sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK073(pu)001:3479: de phyir skas gdangs lta bu ste //
NK073(pu)001:3480: thabs mkhas 'di yis gzhan pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3481: thabs la brten nas mos bcug cing //
NK073(pu)001:3483: rang sa thob las ngo bo nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3484: gcig par smra ba mun sprul pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3485: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3487: // 'gro ba lam log lam stor ba //
NK073(pu)001:3488: lnga dang lnga rnams bkri ba'i phyir /
NK073(pu)001:3489: mi gnyis lam chog 'di bgyis pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3490: ngal ba'i dge rtsas kun grol shog /
NK073(pu)001:3491: byang chub zhor byed khe grags gnyer //
NK073(pu)001:3492: bcud chen 'dzag ci gzhog ngom can //
NK073(pu)001:3493: gtsug rgyal sgeg mo 'jag skyel dang //
NK073(pu)001:3494: nal bya lta bu'i lkog g.yem sogs //
NK073(pu)001:3495: tshul bsrung dam la mi gnas dang //
NK073(pu)001:3496: gsang ba'i gzhung la sran mi tshugs //
NK073(pu)001:3497: gzhug mang bsgrub la yid ches dka' //
NK073(pu)001:3498: bla ma spyi bos mi len cing //
NK073(pu)001:3499: zhe nas skur zhing yod la'ang skur //
NK073(pu)001:3500: snod med rnams la ma 'phrad cig /
NK073(pu)001:3501: mang yul khri babs su gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras bsgyur ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:3502: lam rnams par bkod pa sangs rgyas gsang ba'i man ngag rdzogs so ////
NK073(pu)001:3505: // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam rnam par bshad pa chung ngu bzhugs so //
NK073(pu)001:3507: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK073(pu)001:3508: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud mchog las //
NK073(pu)001:3509: skal macha ga dbang mchog lnga ldan pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3510: dam pa'i yul lnga mthong goms mthar //
NK073(pu)001:3511: byed phyir mtshan nyid gsum brjod bya //
NK073(pu)001:3513: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK073(pu)001:3514: nus mthu can gyur bde gshegs rigs //
NK073(pu)001:3515: yan lag 'byung ba'i gzhi ru dgod //
NK073(pu)001:3516: de la sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor rgyu bshad pa //
NK073(pu)001:3517: dbang po yul du snang ba kun //
NK073(pu)001:3518: yul rnams yod pa ma yin te //
NK073(pu)001:3519: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3520: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:3521: dang po pa yi brtag gzhir rung //
NK073(pu)001:3523: nges pa gsum ste thog ma'i tshe //
NK073(pu)001:3524: so sor rtogs rgyu gzhung mthun pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:3525: dbang mchog tshig yul byas la brten //
NK073(pu)001:3526: phyes pas rgyu byas bsam rtog tshe //
NK073(pu)001:3527: gzhung las grags pa'i gtan tshigs lnga //
NK073(pu)001:3528: sngon 'byung rjes sogs las nyid dang //
NK073(pu)001:3529: mi mthun mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gces //
NK073(pu)001:3530: des na rang spyi'i mtshan yul la //
NK073(pu)001:3531: bshes gnyen bdag po rim de thag /
NK073(pu)001:3532: dang bas 'dod dang bag chags rgyud //
NK073(pu)001:3533: shes rab spyan mchog rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3534: gdod nas shes rab lnga yin mtshungs //
NK073(pu)001:3535: zhes smos la sogs lhan cig byed //
NK073(pu)001:3536: de dag sgo nas 'tshol byed pa //
NK073(pu)001:3537: kun tu rgyu bzhin gdod smon byed //
NK073(pu)001:3538: de yis gzung 'dzin spyod yul mtha' //
NK073(pu)001:3539: yod med lung du ma bstan pas //
NK073(pu)001:3542: 'on kyang gnyis rdzogs gnyis med don //
NK073(pu)001:3543: kun yin gang yang min pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3544: phyogs bral phyogs bdag bsam brjod 'das //
NK073(pu)001:3545: thams cad mkhyen don bco lnga gcod //
NK073(pu)001:3546: sems chos ye nas dbyer med phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3547: brgyad drug shes pa shes rab mchog /
NK073(pu)001:3548: nges pa nyid du rgyal bas gsungs //
NK073(pu)001:3550: ngo bos 'brel phyir gzhi nyid nas //
NK073(pu)001:3552: la la thun mong lam rnams nas //
NK073(pu)001:3554: kha cig sems brgyad nas rgyud de //
NK073(pu)001:3555: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed nas //
NK073(pu)001:3556: thun mong mchog lam sbyangs pas 'phrad //
NK073(pu)001:3557: thun mong sa mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK073(pu)001:3558: yang dag sku gsung thugs bco lngas //
NK073(pu)001:3559: byin rlabs 'tshams par mos snang bas //
NK073(pu)001:3561: tha ma'i tshe na gsung lnga yis //
NK073(pu)001:3562: dngos ston sngon byung lam zhes bya //
NK073(pu)001:3564: mos pa tha dad dbang gis na //
NK073(pu)001:3565: bde gshegs sku lnga'i gsung tshul gyis //
NK073(pu)001:3566: so sor 'tshams pa ra gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)001:3567: bskal pa gsum nas sbyangs pa yi //
NK073(pu)001:3568: zab mo gsang thos bzod thob des //
NK073(pu)001:3569: chos sku'i gsung gi tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:3570: brjod med don gyis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)001:3571: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)001:3572: dgongs dang brda yis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)001:3573: sprul pa tshig gi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)001:3574: brjod pa'i tshig gis smel bar bya //
NK073(pu)001:3575: mngon par byang chub gsung ji bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3576: rig pa'i rlabs kyis gtan la dbab //
NK073(pu)001:3577: rdo rje sku yi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)001:3578: gnyis med mtha' bral don gyis dbab //
NK073(pu)001:3579: la la ngo bo nyid gsung ltar //
NK073(pu)001:3580: snang srid mthong thos nyid kyis 'bebs //
NK073(pu)001:3581: gsang ba'i sku yi gsung lta bur //
NK073(pu)001:3582: spyod pa thabs kyis phebs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3583: la la sngon 'byung bstan pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3584: ji bzhin don dam nges pa'i tshig /
NK073(pu)001:3585: rang rkyen mtshan ma'i gtan tshigs dang //
NK073(pu)001:3586: ldem dgongs sbyor pa'i gtan tshigs dang //
NK073(pu)001:3587: bkri drong brgyud pa'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK073(pu)001:3588: so so'i blo la nges byed cing //
NK073(pu)001:3589: brtags yul yongs su gzhig byed phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3590: de dag las kyis gtan tshigs 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3591: de na gtan tshigs dbang btsan par //
NK073(pu)001:3592: gtan tshigs ma gyur gang yang med //
NK073(pu)001:3593: de la re zhig tshig dbang du //
NK073(pu)001:3595: dbab med ston pa'ang de yis de //
NK073(pu)001:3596: mthong rnyed byed phyir dgos yod la //
NK073(pu)001:3597: so sor rtog pa'i yul du 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3598: 'tshol tshe dgos phyir de ltar nges //
NK073(pu)001:3599: de la gcig shos thun mong mchog /
NK073(pu)001:3600: thun mong grags pa'i rnam bzhi sogs //
NK073(pu)001:3601: thun mong min pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK073(pu)001:3602: tshig don mthun par 'bebs pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3603: gtan tshigs don tshig mi mthun pas //
NK073(pu)001:3605: dang po tha snyad gtan la 'bebs //
NK073(pu)001:3606: de bzhin nyid 'bebs ngag mnyam rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:3607: bden bdag gnyis med la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)001:3608: gnyis pa ci yang ma yin la //
NK073(pu)001:3609: ci yang yin dang grub ma grub //
NK073(pu)001:3610: de sogs don 'dod ci yang min //
NK073(pu)001:3611: phyir yin phyir min phyir ma grub //
NK073(pu)001:3612: phyir brjod gtan tshigs la sogs pas //
NK073(pu)001:3613: mi 'dra ltos rgyu ngo bo'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3614: de dag gtan tshigs 'gyur bar nges //
NK073(pu)001:3615: de bas skabs 'dir de la brten //
NK073(pu)001:3616: de de'i yul dang shes pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3618: med na mi 'byung tshul nyid dang //
NK073(pu)001:3619: de ma grub pas de ldog dang //
NK073(pu)001:3620: snang ba rang snang thabs chen dang //
NK073(pu)001:3621: snang bzhin ma grub shes rab nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3622: bar ma sems rtogs rnam par mthar //
NK073(pu)001:3623: lnga bzhi gnyis sogs snga phyir 'phel //
NK073(pu)001:3625: skabs skabs nyid du the tshom med //
NK073(pu)001:3626: de mthar bzhi mthas gdeng ldan pas //
NK073(pu)001:3627: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis med par //
NK073(pu)001:3628: de bzhin nyid du rdo rje'i rigs //
NK073(pu)001:3629: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK073(pu)001:3630: dmigs med tshul du rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)001:3631: byang chub sems snang thams cad ni //
NK073(pu)001:3632: shin tu brtags dka' gting zab pas //
NK073(pu)001:3633: ma dmigs mi dmigs dmigs su med //
NK073(pu)001:3634: sems nyid de ni ji lta bu //
NK073(pu)001:3635: byang chub de ni sems yin no //
NK073(pu)001:3636: sems dang byang chub gnyis med pas //
NK073(pu)001:3637: sems can ma lus thams cad dang //
NK073(pu)001:3638: dus gsum chos rnams thams cad yin //
NK073(pu)001:3639: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK073(pu)001:3640: sems dang byang chub nyid du 'ub //
NK073(pu)001:3641: yangs shing rgya che lhun grub ni //
NK073(pu)001:3642: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas dag /
NK073(pu)001:3643: dag rtog nyid kyang dbyings nyid yin //
NK073(pu)001:3644: 'di ni rdo rje mnyam yin no //
NK073(pu)001:3645: byang chub sems zhes brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:3647: rtog med rang rig kho na tsam //
NK073(pu)001:3648: sangs rgyas sems can sems la gnas //
NK073(pu)001:3649: mnyam pa'i don nyid ji ltar bu //
NK073(pu)001:3650: mnyam nyid rang bzhin gang yang min //
NK073(pu)001:3651: mnyam dang rtog pa gnyis ka med //
NK073(pu)001:3652: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3653: sgyu ma'i mig yor tshul shes pas //
NK073(pu)001:3654: gnyis ka rang rig nyid du 'dus //
NK073(pu)001:3655: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:3656: rang bzhin ye nas dag pa yin //
NK073(pu)001:3657: sus kyang ma byas ngang gis gsal //
NK073(pu)001:3659: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul ni //
NK073(pu)001:3660: kun dang thun mong de ma yin //
NK073(pu)001:3661: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul te //
NK073(pu)001:3662: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK073(pu)001:3663: thams cad ma lus gcig pa'i ngang //
NK073(pu)001:3664: lta dang blta bar bya med par //
NK073(pu)001:3665: ye shes sgron ma sbreng bas ni //
NK073(pu)001:3666: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK073(pu)001:3667: thams cad ma lus don 'byung ba //
NK073(pu)001:3668: tshig gis mtshon las gud na med //
NK073(pu)001:3669: sgra nyid don gyi ngo bo min //
NK073(pu)001:3670: don nyid sgra las gud na med //
NK073(pu)001:3671: sgra dang tshig tu brjod pa ni //
NK073(pu)001:3672: yang dag don gyi snying po min //
NK073(pu)001:3673: ming tshig sgra la mi brten par //
NK073(pu)001:3674: blo yis gting du go bar byos //
NK073(pu)001:3675: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK073(pu)001:3676: dang po don rtogs mtha' mi gtong //
NK073(pu)001:3677: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:3678: skye bar bgrangs kyang lhung mi 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:3679: tshong dpon lam mtha'i bsam pa bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:3681: shes rab dang po smos pa gsum //
NK073(pu)001:3683: bar chad med sbyor shes rab rim //
NK073(pu)001:3684: mtha' gsum kun 'gro mi g.yo dang //
NK073(pu)001:3685: mthar phyin shes rab rim shes dgos //
NK073(pu)001:3686: bdag nyid ma mthong shes rgyud ma 'byor bas //
NK073(pu)001:3687: gzhan du tshol zhing sems can rmongs pa yis //
NK073(pu)001:3688: bstan kyang ma thos mtshon kyang ma mthong bas //
NK073(pu)001:3689: bdag dang gzhan du 'tshol bas 'tshang mi rgya //
NK073(pu)001:3690: mi g.yo bkod pa bsrung bar rol //
NK073(pu)001:3691: mdzad pa gnas stob rim don gnyer //
NK073(pu)001:3693: dam tshig phrin las spyod pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3694: mchod pa dbang dang sgrub pa dang //
NK073(pu)001:3695: phyag rgya sngags kyi lta ba rnams //
NK073(pu)001:3696: shes chod bya yi tshig tsam min //
NK073(pu)001:3697: de bas lam 'di'i bye brag mthong //
NK073(pu)001:3698: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK073(pu)001:3699: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK073(pu)001:3700: de nyid ma bcos mi g.yo'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3701: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK073(pu)001:3702: de nyid kun gsal ye shes phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3703: de ni kun tu snang gi ngang //
NK073(pu)001:3704: 'bras bu'i chos rnams kun dngos phyir //
NK073(pu)001:3705: de ni rgyu yi rim pa ldan //

NK073(pu)001:3715: rang rig lta ba dam tshig yin //

NK073(pu)001:3722: thig le chen po'i ngang du gsal //

NK073(pu)001:3725: spyod pa rnam pa gnyis po yang //
NK073(pu)001:3726: thig le chen po'i ngang nges phyir //

NK073(pu)001:4030: rig rgyud mtshan dang gzugs ris med //
NK073(pu)001:4031: de yang de phyir rgyal ba'i rgyud //
NK073(pu)001:4032: gnas 'gyur cha gzugs ga la yod //
NK073(pu)001:4033: 'on te thams cad gcig zhe na //
NK073(pu)001:4035: dogs pa skye ba kun gzhi'i sems //

NK073(pu)001:4037: mtshan nyid mtha' bral bkod med pa'i //
NK073(pu)001:4040: ye shes lnga'am rang byung gi //

NK073(pu)001:4042: de phyir gcig mthar ltung ba med //
NK073(pu)001:4043: rgyal ba de nyid rin chen ltar //
NK073(pu)001:4044: kun gyi spyi gzugs yin pa'i phyir //
NK073(pu)001:4045: rgyal tshab lnga la ris yod kyi //
NK073(pu)001:4046: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas la med //
NK073(pu)001:4047: rgyal ba kun kyang dus gsum chos //
NK073(pu)001:4048: bdag phyir kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK073(pu)001:4049: cha gnyis yod par gang gis rung //
NK073(pu)001:4050: yod na bdag nyid chen po rdzun //
NK073(pu)001:4051: 'od zer nyi ma'am shing me bzhin //
NK073(pu)001:4052: ngo bo gcig la ye shes rgyud //
NK073(pu)001:4053: so so yin na sprul pa yang //
NK073(pu)001:4054: gdul bya gcig la mthun par snang //
NK073(pu)001:4055: sems dpa' che dang khyad med 'gyur //
NK073(pu)001:4057: gzhi don lung rig kun dang 'gal //
NK073(pu)001:4059: de phyir shing gi me dpung ltar //
NK073(pu)001:4060: ye shes ston pa bkri drangs phyir //
NK073(pu)001:4061: rung gis yang dag nges pa med //
NK073(pu)001:4062: de bas sangs rgyas yang sangs rgyas //
NK073(pu)001:4063: log par rtogs brtags rnam dag cing //
NK073(pu)001:4064: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK073(pu)001:4065: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK073(pu)001:4066: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK073(pu)001:4067: mtho dman kun gyi gzugs snang yang //
NK073(pu)001:4068: bla med byang chub skur snang ba //
NK073(pu)001:4069: me long lta bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK073(pu)001:4070: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK073(pu)001:4071: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK073(pu)001:4072: byang chub snying po'i ngang nyid du //
NK073(pu)001:4074: de phyir yul med thams cad mkhyen //
NK073(pu)001:4075: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK073(pu)001:4076: rtog pa med par re ba skong //
NK073(pu)001:4077: nyi zla chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar //
